well_activity_remarks_html:
WELL_NAME API12 WAR_START_DT TEXT_REMARK
0 001 608074030500 2010-05-28 05/28 - Arrived on location & began setting anchors. 05/29 - Per NTL No. 2010-N04; operations suspended. Began anchor recovery.
1 001 608074030500 2010-05-30 05/30 - Completed anchor recovery operations. Per NTL No. 2010-N04; operations suspened; moved off location.
2 001 608074030500 2012-06-23 06/23 - Arrived on location at 11:00 hours.
3 001 608074030500 2012-06-24 06/24 - Worked on maintenance projects. Deployed beacons w/ ROV @ 11:00 hrs & performed AB/LB calibration @ well center @ 14:31 hrs. Moved 500' orth of location @ 18:15 hrs. Mud Pump pop-off = ~90% complete; Scalper shaker installation = ~40% complete; BOP work scope = ~15% complete. 06/25 - Cont'd w/ rig projects / OES inspection & BOP work scope. Changed oil & filters on TDS. Rebuilt swivel packing f/ TDS. Cont'd maintenance on standpipe manifold valves & mud pumps. Prep'd #5 generator to be installed. 06/26 - Cont'd w/ rig projects. Performed blackout recovery test. Changed cables on foxhole. Removed air boxes to allow for removal of generator. Offloaded tubulars / WBM f/ Genie Lab. 06/27 - Completed fox hole cable change-out. Removed & began installing new generator #5. OES to continue w/ handling gear inspections. Spotted & began plumbing in scalper shakers. 06/28 - Completed insalling swivel packing. Changed pump liners to 6". Finished generator #5 installation. Cont'd plumbing in scalper shakers. Worked boats as required. Cont'd OES inspections. 06/29 - Completed generator #5 installation. Cont'd plumbing in scalper shakers. Worked boats as required. Cont'd OES inspections. Changed cmt manifold valves. Attempted to install kelly hose guide rail (had to take down & modify / fix). 06/30 - Cont'd kelly hose guide rail installation in derrick; plumbing in scalper shakers & OES inspections. Changed liners on #1 mud pump. Maintenance on mud pump motors.
4 001 608074030500 2012-07-01 07/01 - Completed kelly hose guide rail installation in derrick. Began PU 6-5/8" drill pipe & drilling BHA. 07/02 - Finished picking up 26" x 32" drill ahead BHA. Ran 36" conductor & began jetting ops. 07/03 - Jetted 36" structural csg & let soak. Released CADA tool & drilled ahead. POOH due to BHI steering head tool failure. 07/04 - Troubleshot BHI tools. TIH & drilled ahead f/ 4765' to 4930'. POOH & changed tool strings. TIH w/ new tools. 07/05 - Drilled ahead f/ 4930' to 6031'. 07/06 - Drilled to section TD @ 6310'. Circ'd hole clean & spotted 10.0 ppg pad mud. RU & ran 28" csg & inner string. MU 28" RT & began TIH w/ csg on landing string. 07/07 - TIH w/ 28" csg; landed & cemented same w/ 5890 cu/ft cmt. Released 28" RT & circ'd wiper ball. TOOH w/ 28" RT. R/B 22" MRLDT. PU 26" BHA; TIH; washed down & tagged firm cmt @ 6080'.
5 001 608074030500 2012-07-08 07/08 - Drilled out cement in 28" shoe track w/ SW & drilled out shoe @ 6176'. Pumped 100 bbl hi-vis & chased w/ 10.5 ppg pad mud & began pump/dump. Reamed thru rathole f/ 6176'-6204'. Drilled to 7620' (section TD); pumping hi-vis sweeps as needed. Began POOH w/ drilling assy. 07/09 - Cont'd POOH & LD BHA. RU & ran 22" csg - 3;203.3' of total csg ran; 70 total jnts (including jewelry). Once land3ed: 18" receptacle @ 7033'; 16" receptacle @ 6555'; shoe @ 7569'. PU HPWH & landed on support plate. Ran -5/8" 34 ppf inner string drill pipe. Troubleshot bridge racker. 07/10 - Completed repairs to bridge racker. Finished running inner string. MU MRLDT & TIH w/ 22" csg. Circ'd hole clean & cemented 22" csg (6020 cu/ft). Est TOC inside csg = 7469'. Displaced w/ SW to spot TOC ~100' above shoe - cmt in place @ 15:29. Released MRLDT & TOOH w/ DP. Slipped/cut drill line. 07/11 - Serviced rig. RU floor for running riser. PU 34# 6-5/8" drill pipe in foxhole. SS cont'd to work on / soak BOP to get ready to run (change shear seal). 07/12 - PU 76 jts of 6-5/8" 34# drill pipe. Moved BOPs to well center and MU to boost jt. Began incline test. 07/13 - Calibrated ERA/ESA & splashed BOPs @ 06:00. Began running marine riser to 2153' (total of 29 jts). Installed bullseye btwn jt 28 & 29. RU to test choke/kill & rigid conduit lines. 07/14 - Finished running marine riser to 4238' (total 59 jts). Installed STR ring halves to TJ in moon pool. Secured mux cable & IWOC cables. Latched TJ to STR ring. Attempted to stab BOPs on wellhead.
6 001 608074030500 2012-07-15 07/15 - Corrected spaceout on marine riser. Reinstalled STR; mux & IWOC cables. Latched BOPs to wellhead. Tested BSRs; connector & VX gasket (pressure tested well head connector to 250 psi low/1000 psi high for 5 mins each - good. Tested BSR to 250 low / 2500 high for 5 mins - good. Performed 22" csg; wellhead connector VX gasket & BSR test to 250 psi low for 5 mins & 2500 psi high for 30 mins - good test.). RD riser handling equip. 07/16 - Cont'd RD riser handling equip. MU 18-1/8" x 21" BHA & TIH w/ Dril-Quip test plug. Performed UPS battery drawdown & began testing BOPs to 250 psi low / 9000 psi high. 07/17 - Finished BOP testing on 6-5/8" drill pipe - Annulars (250 psi / 3500 psi); Rams (250 psi / 9000 psi). Functioned lower annular on Yellow POD & observed leak. Troubleshot. RU o pull marine riser. 07/18 - Unlatched f/wellhead & pulled marine riser. 07/19 - Finished pulling BOPs on marine riser f/ 1403' to 128'. Pulled BOPs thru splash zone & landed on beams @ 05:00 hrs. RU riser torque wrench & bread out boost joint f/ LMRP. Transported BOP stack f/ well center to starboard side. Troubleshoot & repaired readback regulator on Yellow POD. Soaked Yellow & Blue PODs. 07/20 - Repaired compression fitting for 5k readback regulator on Yellow POD and soaked Yellow/Blue PODs. Skid BOPsto well center & connected Boost Jt to LMRP. Calibrated ERA/ESA; splashed BOPs & ran marine riser to 728' (total 10 jts). 07/21 - Cont'd running BOPs on marine riser to 4238'. PU landing jnt & latched TJ to STR ring. Unlatched STR f/ diverter housing & slacked off to moon pool. Installed SALT ring hoses to TJ jnt.
7 001 608074030500 2012-07-22 07/22 - Latched BOPs to 18-3/4" wellhead. Closed BSR w/ ROV; performed csg & wellhead connector test. Tested auto shear on deadman to 250 psi / 1000 psi for 5 mins on chart. Flow tested diverter & RD riser handling equip. Troubleshot subsea flow meter issue. 07/23 - TIH w/ 18-1/8" x 21" BHA & tested BOPs Annulars (250 psi / 3500 psi); Rams (250 psi / 9000 psi). POOH; LD test plug & TIH w/ wear sleeve to 316'. Tested wellhead connector against BSR to 250 psi / 2680 psi for 5 mins on chart - good test. NOTE: On 07/23/12 @ 18:49 hours; verbal approval granted from David LeLeux (BSEE Lafayette District) for wellhead connector test to 2680 psi in lieu of 9000 psi. 07/24 - RIH to TOC @ 7;465'. Displaced to 10.0 ppg SBM. Drilled shoe track & WR 26" rathole to 7;620'; drilled 10' new formation to 7;630'. Performed FIT to 11.6 ppg EMW. 07/25 - Cleaned out rathole f/ 7569' to 7630'. Drilled to 9633'; while weighting up to 10.7 ppg. 07/26 - Drilled to 11;104'; weighting up to 10.8 ppg. 07/27 - Drilled to 11;170'. C&CM to 11.0 ppg. Tripped into csg & backreamed cmt sheath f/ 7569' to 7419'. CBU & POOH. 07/28 - PU 18" shoe track assy. MU & began running 18" 117# P-110 Hydril csg. MU Dril-Quip hgr & TIH w/ 6-5/8" drill pipe.
8 001 608074030500 2012-07-29 07/29 - Finished running 18" csg to 11;030' & set hgr in 18" profile. Cemented 18" w/ 150 bbls (841 cu/ft) & displaced plugs. Set hgr seal assy & tested to 3400 psi. 07/30 - Finished POOH w/ liner running tool. Cleaned & serviced rig. MU 16-1/2" x 19" BHA & TIH w/ test plug. Set test plug & began testing BOPs; Annulars (250 psi / 3500 psi); Rams (250 psi / 9000 psi). 07/31 - Finished testing BOPs & wellhead connector. POOH w/ test plug. Tested 18"/22" csg & BSR to 250 psi / 3400 psi f/ 5 mins & cont'd csg test to 3400 psi f/ 30 mins on chart. TIH w/ 6-5/8" 27.7# drill pipe to 4144'. Serviced rig & slipped & cut drill line. 08/01 - TIH to TOC @ 10;871' while picking up 6-5/8" 27# & 34# drill pipe. Drilled float equip & 10' of new formation to 11;180'. Pulled into the shoe & CBU @ 11;030' to top of wellhead. 08/02 - Performed FIT to 16.0 ppg EMW. Drilled to 11;280'. PU to make connection @ 11;280' & stalled out. Attempted to work pipe free - set jars w/ 50k lb down - jarred pipe free & pulled into shoe. W&R tight hole f/ 11;030' to 11;280' while raising MW to 13.0 ppg. C&CM @ 11;280' - con'td to raise MW to 12.5 ppg. Drilled f/ 11;280' to 11;729' while raising MW to 13.5 ppg. 08/03 - Drilled & surved f/ 11;729' to 13;314'. 08/04 - Drill f/ 13;314' to 14;047'. Stopped drilling & CBU @ 14;047' in preparation for Tropical Storm Ernesto. POOH to 6731'; MU hang off tool & special BOP test tool. RIH to 9;377'. NOTE: Received verbal approval f/ BSEE Lafayette District (Marty Rinaudo) for storm preparation operations and to test the cavity between the lower variable rams & top of the test plug to 1000 psi.
9 001 608074030500 2012-08-05 08/05 - Hang off string in WH. Performed positive test on test plug & released f/ hang off tool. PU above BOP & performed inflow test. Peformed rig maint & monitored Tropical Storm Ernesto. 08/06 - Cont'd performing rig servicing & maintenance. Began BOP tests while monitoring weather. 08/07 - Completed BOP testing - tested Annulars to 250 psi low / 3500 psi high; and Rams to 250 psi low / 9000 psi high. POOH to LD hang off tool. RIH & drilled f/ 14;047' to 14;450'. 08/08 - Drilled f/ 14;450' to 15;889'. PU landing string offline. 08/09 - Drilled f/ 15;889' to 16;165'. Decision made to trip for BHA due to increase in torque & reduction in ROP. POOH. 08/10 - Cont'd POOH. Inspected & LD BHA. MU & RIH w/ new BHA. Drilled f/ 16;15' to 16;186'. 08/11 - Drilled f/ 16;168' to 17;930'.
10 001 608074030500 2012-08-12 08/12 - Drilled & surveyed f/ 17;930' to 19;680'. 08/13 - Drilled f/ 19;680' to 21;482'. NOTE: Flushed choke & kill lines @ 22:00 hrs w/ 14.7 ppg SOBM. 08/14 - Drilled f/ 21;482' to 22;036'. Took kick on connection. SWI. Circ'd out kick over chokes using Driller's method. Monitored well. Weighted up to 15.1 ppg & circ'd over choke. 08/15 - Completed circulating 15.1 ppg SOBM around. Monitored well to ensure it is static. NOTE: Functioned BOPs f/ Driller's panel; Yellow POD; SEM B. Functioned diverter f/ both panels. CBU @ 22;036'. Drilled ahead to 22;204'. 08/16 - Drilled f/ 22;204' to 23;291'; increasing MW f/ 15.1 ppg to 15.2 ppg. Increased MW f/ 15.2 ppg to 15.4 ppg & began experiencing losses. At 23:30 began losing mud. Reduced pump rate to 600 GPM to minimize losses while preparing LCM pill. Total losses at midnight - 93 bbls. 08/17 - Displaced riser to 15.3 ppg mud. Pumped LCM pill and drilled ahead to 23;320' while circulating pill down. Monitored losses & spotted 100 bbl pill on btm; pulled above it & let it soak - did not cure losses. Tripped back to btm & prep'd another LCM pill. POOH f/ 23;291' to 22;289' & allowed formation to heal - losing @ 20bbl/hr. NOTE: total losses since midnight = 2;912 bbls. Closed annular & closed choke allowing formation to heal. Opened choke every hour to monitor loss rate. Loss rate consistently 210/bbl hr. Loss total of 68.5 bbls. Wellhead pressure @ 3281 psi. Opened both choke & kill fail safes & attempted to fill annulus f/ mini-trip tank - lost 66 bbls; loss rate 195 bb;/hr; wellhead pressure dropped f/ 3275 psi to 3268 psi. Riser level static (monitored on trip tank). Closed both choke & kill fail safes to allow formation to heal while monitoring wellhead pressure. Initial WH pressure 3268 psi; dropped to 3237 psi by 22:00 hrs. Opened annular & attempted to fill annulus w/ trip tank & pumping down boost line @ 6 bpm - no returns. Lost 295 bbls. Closed annular & filled up riser. Opened annular & TIH f/ 22;222' to 23;134' closing annular after every stand run & filling riser w/ trip tank & boost pump to keep well full. Lost 600 bbls during TIH. NOTE: Received approval from Mr. David Leleux to delay shear ram function until drill string is pulled clear of BOP -- e-mail approval attached. 08/18 - Monitored riser on trip tank with annular closed while M&P 150 bbls of 100ppb Foam-A Sqz pill - no relief. Began mixing 300 bbls of 100 ppb Form-A Sqz pill. Total losses for event = 5151 bbls.
11 001 608074030500 2012-08-19 08/19 - Pumped 300 bbls Form-A Sqz pill & let soak to cure losses - no change in loss rate. Pumped 250 bbls of cmt & allowed to set-up. 08/20 - WOC while monitoring wellhead & drill pipe pressure & riser on the trip tank (static). Attempted to free sring w/ no success (unable to get jars to stroke). Cont'd to work string. 08/21 - Cont'd working pipe in atempt to free w/ no success. Dropped WIPR severing tool. Unable to pressure up to fire. Began RU EL. NOTE: Marty Rinaudo (BSEE Lafayette District) granted approval to defer BOP test until 1st trip out of the hole. 08/22 - Finished RU EL & made fishing run w/ no success; pressured up & fired WIPR sub. Ran free poin & RIH w/ severing tool & severed string -- pipe free. Began POOH w/ EL. 08/23 - RD WL. Pumped Swell LCM pill & 150 bbl of cmt. POOH to 18;812' & slipped/cut drill line. TIH to TOF & prep'd for KO plug. 1. RIH with cementing stinger to open hole. Pump equivalent cement volume to fill open
hole volume.
     a. Pump 2 x 1000' cement plugs f/ TD to 31;500'.
     b. Pump 450' cement plug f/ 31;500' to 31;050'.
2. Run 9-5/8" EZSV on wireline to ~31;000' and set.
     a. Pressure test to 1;500 psi.
3. POOH w/ setting tool. RD wireline unit.
4. RIH w/ 13-5/8" FasDrill to the 11-7/8" liner top and set at ~22;500'.
     a. Pressure test to 1;500 psi & weight test w/ 15;000 lbs.
        i. Ensure that the pressure does not drop more than 10% in 15 minutes.
5. Pump 300' balanced cement plug above the FasDrill retainer f/ 22;500' to 22;200'.
6. PU above TOC & circulate drill pipe wiper ball.
7. POOH
8. RIH w/ 13-5/8" FasDrill to 5;400' (+/-1;000' BML) and set.
9. Negative test to SW gradient using Cobalt Standard Operating Procedure DRLGOM-0900-PRC-0192.
10. Displace 15.7 ppg SOBM f/ top of plug to surface w/ SW as per MI Swaco displacement procedure.
11. Spot 500' cement plug on top of retainer.
12. PU above TOC & circulate drill pipe wiper ball.

Cementer bled back 2 more bbls; pressure dropped f/ 900 to 570 psi. WOC. Monitor well on trip tank. Well static. Cementer bled off pressure to 0 psi. 21 bbls total bled back. Monitored well on trip tank. Well static. RD cmt line & ctrl lines f/ cmt head. Set & tested 18" seal assy. Closed upper pipe rams; cementer pressured up down choke line to 3500 psi for 5 min. Monitored for leaks at surface. Good test. Pumped 12 bbls; bled back 12 bbls. Broke out cmt head. Installed nerf ball & circ one string volume w/ 13.2 ppg SBM. Pumped 65 bbls 15.3 ppg SBM slug. Flow checked well after pumping slug. Well static. TOOH f/ 8200' to 132' w/ 6-5/8" 43 ppf DP. Flow checked well. Static. 

5/25/15 - TOOH w/ 6-5/8" 43 ppf DP & LD 18" liner hanger running tool. MU 16-1/2" x 19" BHA to 1028'. TIH w/ 16-1/2" x 19" BHA on 6-5/8" 34 ppf DP f/ 1028' to 4813'. Proper displacement observed. Monitored well on trip tank. Hung off blocks. Cut 133' of 2-1/8" drill line. Unhung blocks. Performed 18" csg test w/ 13.2 ppg SBM against LBSR to 250 psi for 5 min & 2260 psi for 30 min. Pumped 21.5 bbls & bled back 21.5 bbls. Good test. Tested UBSR to 2260 psi for 5 min w/ 13.2 ppg SBM. Good test. Functioned all BSR/CSR f/ driller's panel; blue pod; SEM A. Monitored well on trip tank. Well static. TIH w/ 16-1/2" x 19" BHA f/ 4318' to 14032'. Set Dril-Quip wear bushing at 4912'. Obtained static temperature reading f/ LWD; 130.2 degrees @ 14032'.
Cycled MWD / turned on tools by pumping 650 gpm / 2400 psi. Pumped 13.2 ppg SBM. Flushed choke; kill; choke manifold & po-boy degasser w/ 13.2 ppg SBM @ 14032'. Took slow pump rates. Located on upper annular w/ 6-5/8" 34 ppf DP on driller's panel; blue pod; SEM A. Performed hard shut in & trapped 200 psi on back side. Staged up pumps to kill rate while maintaining 200 psi on choke panel. Then closed choke while slowing pumps maintaining 200 psi until well was shut in. Monitored well on active
gain / loss. Monitored riser w/ trip tank. Well static. TIH w/ 6-5/8" 43 ppf DP. Tagged w/ 10k lbs down @ 14066'. Picked up & retagged @ same depth. W&R to 14076'. W&R f/ 14076' to 14088'. 

5/26/15 - Drilled out cmt f/ 14088' to 14537'. Drilled out of shoe @ 14537'. Monitored well on active gain / loss & on trip tank during connections. Well static. W&R cmt f/ 14537' to 14550' & cleaned rat hole f/ 14550' to 14725' w/ 13.3 ppg SBM. Drilled new formation f/ 14725' to 14735'. CBU above BOPs w/ 13.3 ppg SBM. Pulled 2 stands f/ 14735' to 14502'. Lined up & broke circ down kill line & string. Performed FIT test against MPR w/ 13.3 ppg SBM to 15.5 ppg EMW / 1671 psi. Pumped 17 bbls & bled back 17 bbls. Shoe TVD 14537'. Pumped up MWD recorded FIT at 700 gpm / 2800 psi (15.70 ppg EMW w/ static MW 13.56 ppg). W&R f/ 14502' to 14714'. Dropped 1-3/4" reamer activation ball. Activated reamer. Pull test reamer to confirm it was open. Drilled vertical hole f/ 14735' to 14914'. 

5/27/15 - Drilled vertical f/ 14914' to 15745'. Increased MW f/ 13.3 to 13.6 ppg while drilling. Flow checked well due to deviation in active gain loss. Spaced out string to hang off position. Monitored hole on trip tank for 15 min; static. Drilled vertical f/ 15745' to 17250'. Increased MW f/ 13.6 to 14.1 ppg while drilling.

5/28/15 - Drilled f/ 17250' to 18680' (TD). C&C mud at 18680'. Spotted 150 bbl of 17.0 ppg pill in rat hole & displaced pill w/ 476 bbls of 14.1 ppg SOBM. TOOH f/ 18680' to 18310'. Function tested BOP f/ yellow pod SEM A. Function tested diverter f/ driller's panel. 

5/29/15 - Held PJSM. TOOH f/ 18310' to 13282'. Hole not taking proper fill. TIH f/ 13282' to 14737'. Monitored hole on trip tank - hole taking proper fill. MU TDX & filled pipe w/ 14.1 ppg SBM. TIH f/ 14737' to 18310'. Monitored hole on trip tank -
static. Washed in hole f/ 18310' to 18680'. CBU @ 18680'. Flow checked hole on trip tank - static. Circ 2 line volumes down kill line & up choke line. Opened test rams & upper annular. Monitored well on trip tank - gained 4.41 bbls in 21 min. Closed upper annular & monitored well on trip tank - static. Opened upper annular & circ @ 18679' weighting up mud to 14.3 ppg.

5/30/15 - Held PJSM. Flow checked - static. Took SCRs w/ 14.3 ppg SOBM. Spotted 150 bbls of 17.0 ppg pill in rathole. TOOH f/ 18680' to 14473'. Proper hole fill observed. Flow checked inside shoe - static. Pumped out of hole using OES DP fill up tool f/ 14466' to 7753'. Circ @ 7753' to clean 16" profile. TOOH f/ 7753' to surface.","WAR_START_DT":"2015-05-24","WELL_NAME":"  003"},{"   ":53,"API12":608074031500,"TEXT_REMARK":"5/31/15 - TOOH w/ BHA to surface. Held PJSM. PU & RIH w/ 16"; 97 ppf; Q-125HP to 8178'. 

6/1/15 - Held PJSM. Cont'd to RIH w/ 16"; 97 ppf; Q-125HP csg f/ 8178' to 10732'. Monitored well on trip tank. Well static. Float collar 85' above shoe. PU Dril-Quip 16" csg hanger & MU same. MU TDX & filled pipe w/ 14.3 ppg SOBM. RIH on 6-5/8" 43 ppf & 47 ppf landing string f/ 10774' to 18468' filling w/ 14.3 ppg SOBM. RU cmt head & cmt lines. Landed 16" csg hanger in adapter profile @ 7758'. Summary: TOL - 7755'; float collar - 18425'; shoe - 18510'. RU ctrl lines for cmt head. Displaced kill line w/ 14.3 ppg.

6/2/15 - Held PJSM. Broke circ w/ 10 bbls of 14.8 ppg tuned spacer III. Tested surface lines to 6000 psi. Held for 5 min. Good test. Pumped remaining 90 bbls of 14.8 ppg tuned spacer III. Launched bottom dart. M&P 1261 sks / 244 bbls / 1370 cuft of Class H. Density 16.4 ppg; yield 1.0862 cuft/sk. Launched top dart. Pumped 25 bbls
of 14.8 ppg tuned spacer followed by 40 bbls of 14.3 ppg SBM. Minimal returns. Turned over to rig & displaced cmt w/ rig pumps w/ 2513 bbls of 14.3 ppg SOBM. Launched bottom wiper plug @ 127 bbls of displacement w/ 3150 psi. Landed bottom wiper plug on float collar @ 2285 bbls pumped w/ 1791 psi. Pumped a total of 2513 bbls of displacement. Did not bump top plug. Minimal returns to surface while displacing cmt. Bled back 7 bbls. Float held. Summary: TOC - 16657'; Cement in Shoe: 160' - 34 bbls / 191 cuft / 176 sks; Cement in Annulus: 1853' - 210 bbls / 1179 cuft / 1085 sks. RD cmt hose & hydraulic control lines. Monitored well on trip tank. Well static. Set 16" seal assy. Tested seal assy against upper annular to 5000 psi using 14.3 ppg SOBM. Held for 5 min. Monitored riser on trip tank. Circ drill string volume w/ wiper ball. TOOH w/ 16" liner RT f/ 7713' to RKB. Found 16" seal assy still on running tool but missing outer lock ring. Cut & slip 153' of drill line. Removed Frank's 18' 1250T bails & installed rig's 12' 1250T drilling bails. MU Dril-Quip mill & flush assy w/ 14-1/2" tooth bit & TIH to 930'.

6/3/15 - Held PJSM. TIH w/ mill & flush assy on 6-5/8" 43 ppf DP f/ 930' to 8000'. Washed & milled 16" hanger seal area at 7755' mill depth. CBU. Mud weight out was 14.3 ppg - no changes in mud properties. Pumped 60 bbls of 16.4 ppg SBM slug & flow checked well. POOH. TIH w/ mill & flush assy w/ string magnets to 8063'. 

6/4/15 - Wash 16" profile w/ Dril-Quip mill & flush adapter @ 7755' (8068' bit depth). CBU. Pump slug & POOH to 7699' while monitoring well on trip tank. Well ballooning @ 30 bbls/hr. POOH to 6685' while monitoring well on trip tank. Observed ballooning rate increase to 36 bbls/hr. TIH to 7303' & monitor well on trip tank. Closed in on lower annular & monitor well. SIDPP 357 psi & SICP 527 psi. (50 bbl slug in drill pipe). Begin weight up of active system f/ 14.3 ppg to 15.7 ppg. Bled off pressure in 10 bbl increments & monitored well on trip tank for 30 min. Observed pressure build up of 9 psi/min to 357 psi. Repeat bleed off & monitored for additional 30 min. Observed pressure build up of 12.7 psi/min to 507 psi. Displaced 15.7 ppg KWM down drill string & up choke line using Wait & Weight method at 40 SPM & 365 psi. Note: Checked for losses when KWM at bit depth (no losses observed). Boost riser w/ 15.7 ppg KWM at 400 GPM & 490 psi. Function test BOPs on 6-5/8" drillpipe using driller's panel on blue pod SEM A.

6/5/15 - Flush bleed line below upper annular w/ 15.7 ppg SBM. Displace kill line to 15.7 ppg. Monitor well on trip tank. Open annular & monitor well on trip tank (well ballooning @ 24 bbl/hr). TIH on 6-5/8" drill pipe to 8063' (7755' mill depth). CBU w/ 15.7 ppg SBM. Cont'd to circ until a consistent 15.7 ppg was surface. Received approval f/ David LeLeux to extend BOP testing until 16" remedial operations are complete. Monitor well on trip tank (well ballooning @ 17 bbl/hr). Boost riser in
stages using 16.0 ppg SBM. Pumped a total of 1065 bbls in riser & observed ballooning rate decrease to 1.5 bbl/hr. Pump out of hole f/ 8063' to 7479'. Monitor well on trip tank (well ballooning @ 9 bbl/hr). POOH wet 5 stands. Flow check well (static). POOH f/ 6818' to surface while spotting 75 bbls of 16.0 ppg SBM in riser. LD Dril-Quip mill & flush adapter (no indication of mill assy reaching seal profile). Monitor well on trip tank (well ballooning @ 3.5 bbl/hr). MU squeeze assy & monitor well on trip tank (well ballooning @ 3 bbl/hr). 

6/6/15 - TIH to 7815' w/ 16" FasDrill on 6-5/8" 43# drill pipe & set same. Shear out of plug w/ 64k overpull & confirm set w/ 30k down. Pull to 7645' & MU cmt stand. Held PJSM. Break circ & test lines to 6000 psi. Establish injection rates at: 1 bbl/min - 1215 psi; 2 bbl/min - 1950 psi; 3 bbl/min - 2575 psi; 4 bbl/min - 3075 psi and 5 bbl/min - 3750 psi. Add surfactant to 16.0 ppg tuned spacer & prepare for cmt job. Open fail safes & take returns up choke line. Pump 80 bbls of 16.0 ppg tuned spacer; 10 bbls of 8.3 ppg water; 24 bbls of 11.33 ppg CaCl; 10 bbls of 8.3 ppg water; 24 bbl of 11.66 ppg Flo-Chek & 10 bbls of 8.3 ppg water. Close fail safe valves. M&P 100 bbls (563.7 cuft) of 16.4 Class H cement (521 sks / 55 bbl mix fluid). Displaced w/ 225 bbls of 15.7 ppg SBM at decreasing rate of 4 - 2-1/4 bbl/min. At 40 bbls into mud displacement; observed pressure abruptly drop f/ 4025 to 2800 psi. Pressures built back to 4765 psi & fell for the duration of the job to 2350 psi. Cement in place at 13:21 hrs. Pressure bled to 925 psi after 5 min & continued to 0 psi. Check for flow on stripping tank (no flow). Open annular; losing fluid at 30 bbl/hr. RD cmt stand & hoses. POOH wet 8 stands f/ 7645' to 6733' & close annular. WOC while monitoring well on trip tank (static). Displaced riser to 15.7 ppg SBM through boost line. ","WAR_START_DT":"2015-05-31","WELL_NAME":"  003"},{"   ":54,"API12":608074031500,"TEXT_REMARK":"6/7/15 - Monitor well on trip tank (static). Cont'd displacing riser to 15.7 ppg SBM
through boost line. Attempt to test 16" TOL. Pressure built to 1849 psi then began injecting. Shut down & monitored pressure. TIH w/ 7 stands of 6-5/8" drill pipe f/ 6767' to 7640'. Install 2 foam wiper balls in drill string. Circ wiper balls down drill string. Wiper balls stuck in FasDrill setting tool. Switch to Halliburton unit & blow wiper balls through setting tool. Wash down while boosting riser. Tag top of cement @ 7719' & confirm w/ 20k down (top of liner 7755'). Closed upper annular. Attempt to establish injection rates by pumping 1-1.5 bbl/min pressuring up in stages to 2200 psi. Monitor pressure losses (30-35 psi/min). Circ w/ 15.7 ppg SBM while boosting riser. Held PJSM. MU cmt stand & hoses. Break circ & test lines to 5000 psi. Bled off pressure. Pump 80 bbls of 16.0 ppg tuned spacer. M&P 80 bbls (449 cuft) of 16.4 Class H cement (415 sks / 44 bbl mix fluid). Pumped 6 bbls of 16.0 ppg tuned spacer. Displaced w/ 175 bbls of 15.7 ppg SBM. Pull 6 stands of 6-5/8" drill pipe f/ 7714' to 6860'. Close upper annular & line up Halliburton to pump down drill string & choke line. In stages squeeze 42 bbls in 16" liner top while monitoring pressure trends. Pressure to 2292 psi & shut down pump. Monitor pressure on drill string.

6/8/15 - Cont'd monitoring squeeze pressure. Pressure fell f/ 2292 psi to 1008 psi in 12 hours. Release pressure & bleed back 6.5 bbls. Circ 2 foam wiper balls down drill string & above BOPs at 905 gpm & 2100 psi. Pump 50 bbl slug of 17.7 ppg. POOH to 5586'. MU BOP test assy. RU chicksan & test hoses. Test BOPs & related equipment on 6-5/8" drill pipe. Test performed f/ driller's panel on blue POD SEM "B" using IPT reference & Halliburton chart.
Test 1: IBV; LIC; MIC; UIC; CMV - 250 / 10000 psi
Test 2: IBV; LIC; LIK; MIC; MIK; UIC; CMV - 250 / 10000 psi
Test 3: IBV; LIC; MIC; UIC; CMV - 250 / 10000 psi
Test 4: IBV; LIC; MIC; UIC; CMV - 250 / 10000 psi
Test 6: UA; IBV; LIC; MIC; UIC; CMV - 250 / 3600 psi
Test 7: UA; LIC; MIC; OBV; UOC; CMV - 250 / 3600 psi
Test 8: LA; LOK; MOK; OBV; UOK; CMV - 250 / 3600 psi
Test 9: LA; LOK; MOK; OBV; UIK; CMV - 250 / 3600 psi
Test 10: UPR; LOC; MOC; UIK; U-IBOP; CMV - 250 / 11100 psi 

6/9/15 - Cont'd testing BOPs & related equipment on 6-5/8" drill pipe. Test performed f/ driller's panel; blue pod SEM "B" using IPT reference & Halliburton chart. Tested rams & fail safe valves to 250 / 11100 psi; annulars to 250 / 3600 psi & kelly hose to 250 / 7000 psi for 5 min. Observed 27 bbl gain in trip tank. Suspended BOP testing & closed upper annular. Found mud weight cut in trip tank f/ 15.7 to 13.8 ppg. Determined supply & return lines f/ trip tank in diverter housing were plugged allowing cleaning water f/ the rig floor to enter trip tank. Cont'd testing BOPs. Tested rams & fail safe valves to 250 / 11100 psi & kelly hose to 250 / 7000 psi for 5 min. POOH on 6-5/8" drill pipe to surface. Function diverter in test mode f/ driller's panel. Remove upper guide arm on main hydra racker. Remove & replace encoder on main hydra tong. Test BSRs w/ 15.7 ppg SBM f/ driller's panel on blue pod SEM "B". Test performed to 250 / 2440 psi for 5 min each using Halliburton & IPT reference. Function BSRs & CSR f/ driller's panel on blue pod SEM "B". 

6/10/15 - MU 14-1/2" cleanout assy & TIH to 1019'. TIH on 6-5/8" drill pipe f/ 1019' & tagged TOC @ 7567' w/ 15k down. Drilled cmt f/ 7567' to TOL @ 7755'. Washed 10' inside liner top to 7765'. Flow check well on trip tank (static). Close upper annular & line up down drill string & choke line. Attempt to test 16" TOL to 2200 psi w/ 15.7 ppg (no test). Displace well at 7755' f/ 15.7 ppg to 14.5 ppg SBM. Flow check well on trip tank (static). Close upper annular & line up down drill string & choke line. Test 16" TOL to 1650 psi w/ 14.5 ppg (good test). W&R f/ 7710' to 7750' encountering several tight spots. Cont'd washing & tag FasDrill plug at 7807'. Close upper annular & line up down drill string & choke line. Test 16" TOL to 2150 psi w/ 14.5 ppg (good test). Drill 16" FasDrill plug f/ 7807' to 7809'. Wash f/ 7809' to 8031' & tagged w/ 20k down. Drill f/ 8031' to 8036'. 

6/11/15 - Cont'd to drill FasDrill plug w/ 14.5 ppg SBM f/ 8036' to 8072'. Made slow to no progress. Flow check well on trip tank (Gaining 3.5 bbls/hr). Shut in well on upper annular & monitor pressures (SICP 366 psi). Pump 15.7 ppg KWM. Max gas of 3
units observed during well kill. No mud cut of gas noted on bottoms up. Displace riser w/ 15.7 ppg SBM. Flush kill line w/ 15.7 ppg.

6/12/15 - Cont'd displacing riser w/ 15.7 ppg SBM. Open annular & monitor well on trip tank (Losing 6 bbl/hr). POOH 5 stands wet f/ 8036' to 7598'. Pump slug & continue POOH f/ 7598' to surface. Observed 14-1/2" bit 3/4" undergauge & missing 3 cones. All 14-3/8" IB stabilizers undergauge & 73lbs of metal recovered on MagnoStar magnet subs. Perform drawworks brake test. Hang off block. Slip & cut 94' of 2-1/8" drill line. Grease & inspect TDX 1250 & traveling equipment. Un-hang block & perform block calibration test. Check crown & floor savers. Secure hangoff line in derrick. Monitor well on trip tank (Losing 2 bbl/hr). PU 13" reverse circulating junk basket & 4 stands of 6-5/8" HWDP. TIH w/ fishing assy to 5242'.

6/13/15 - TIH w/ 13" reverse circulating junk basket f/ 5242' to 8005'. W&R to 8072'. Observed tight spots at 8037' & 8053'. Pulled above tight spots. Dropped 2-1/4" steel ball. Ream to TOF at 8072'. Observed tight spot at 8053' & worked through. Circulated over fish. POOH w/ fishing assy. Hole took ~4 bbl/hr fluid during trip out. Note: Chunk of cement & small piece of elastomer found in junk basket. Did not recover bit cones. MU 14-1/2" XR+C bit cleanout assy & TIH on 6-5/8" drill pipe to 1236'. Function test BSRs & CSR f/ bridge panel on yellow pod SEM "B". Cont'd TIH w/ cleanout assy f/ 1236' to 7947'. Set wear sleeve in wellhead. Hole took ~2-3 bbl/hr during trip in. W&R f/ 7947' to 8069'. Observed tight spot at 8035'. No overpull noted while POOH. No gas or mud cut on bottoms up. Flow check well on trip tank (static). Pump slug & POOH to 7649'. ","WAR_START_DT":"2015-06-07","WELL_NAME":"  003"},{"   ":55,"API12":608074031500,"TEXT_REMARK":"6/14/15 - POOH w/ 14-1/2" XR+C cleanout assy. Recovered 60 lbs of metal on MagnoStar magnet subs. Hole took 1 bbl/hr during trip out. Monitor well on trip tank (losing 2 bbls/hr) while reconfiguring BHA for next fishing run. TIH w/ 14-1/2" junk mill & boot baskets on 6-5/8" drill pipe to 8005' while monitoring well on trip tank (losing 1 bbl/hr). Wash f/ 8005' & tagged obstruction at 8033'. Ream f/ 8033' to 8067'. No losses or gains observed while reaming. Flow checked well on trip tank (static). Pump slug & POOH f/ 8067' to 4320' while monitoring well on trip tank (losing 1 bbl/hr).

6/15/15 - POOH w/ 14-1/2" junk mill & boot baskets (losing 1 bbl/hr). Cutrite on bottom mill was 5/8" undergauge & 1/8"-1/4" under on OD. One stabilizer blade on the mill was lost in hole. Recovered 55 lbs of metal on MagnoStar magnet subs & cup full of metal in boot baskets. TIH w/ 12-1/8" junk mill w/ 14-1/2" string mill (6' behind junk mill) to 4678' (losing 2 bbl/hr). WOW. Well static. Cont'd TIH w/ junk mill assy f/ 4678' to 7763' while monitoring well on trip tank (losing 1-2 bbl/hr). Set wear sleeve in wellhead. Wash f/ 7763' & tagged obstruction at 8037'. Ream w/ 15.7 ppg SBM f/ 8037' to 8069'. No losses or gains observed while reaming. 

6/16/15 - Cont'd to W&R w/ 12-1/8" junk mill & 14-1/2" string mill to 8070' using 15.7 ppg SBM. No losses or gains observed while reaming. Flow check well on trip tank (static). POOH w/ fishing assy f/ 8070' to 7397'. Function test BOPs on 6-5/8" drill pipe using driller's panel on blue pod SEM "B". Cont'd POOH w/ junk mill f/ 7397' to surface (losing 1-2 bbl/hr). Junk mill was 1/8" under gauge & cored on the bottom. String mill was in gauge. Recovered 64 lbs of metal on MagnoStar magnet subs. Held PJSM. TIH w/ bore protector on 6-5/8" drill pipe to 4836' (losing 1 bbl/hr). Line up & pump down C&K lines. Land bore protector in wellhead observing 35 psi increase in pump pressure. Slack off 20k & rotate to set at 4915'. Pump slug & POOH to surface. MU 13-7/8" flat bottom fishing magnet BHA & TIH to 2593'.

6/17/15 - Cont'd TIH w/ 13-7/8" flat bottom fishing magnet on 6-5/8" drill pipe f/ 2593' to 7989' (losing 1 bbl/hr). Wash f/ 7989' to 8069' w/ 15.7 ppg SBM. Washed to 8069'. Flow check well on trip tank (static). Pump 40 bbl slug of 17.7 ppg. POOH w/ 13-7/8" flat bottom fishing magnet. Recovered 32 lbs of metal on MagnoStar magnet subs & 3 lbs on flat bottom magnet. Clean rig floor while monitoring well on trip tank (losing 1 bbl/hr). MU 6-5/8" mule shoe; 14-1/2" string mill & jar assy (losing 3 bbl/hr). TIH w/ mule shoe assy on 6-5/8" drill pipe to 110'.

6/18/15 - Held PJSM. Cont'd to TIH w/ mule shoe assy on 6-5/8" 34 ppf DP f/ 110' to 8069'. Monitor well on trip tank - gave proper displacement. Attempted to work mule shoe assy past 8069' w/ no success. Tagged obstruction at 8069'. Pumped 40 bbls of 17.7 ppg SBM slug. POOH w/ mule shoe assy on 6-5/8" 34 ppf DP f/ 8069' to 785'. Monitor well on the trip tank. Lost 14.5 bbls total during trip. Held PJSM. TOOH w/ mill assy. Held PJSM. Hung off blocks. Slip & cut 116' of drill line. Unhung block. Calibrated block & performed brake test. TIH w/ bailer assy to 2361'. 

6/19/15 - Held PJSM. Cont'd to TIH w/ 12-1/4" hydrostatic bailer on 6-5/8" 34 ppf DP f/ 2361' to 8069'. Fill pipe every 10 stds w/ 15.7 ppg SBM. Well took proper displacement on trip tank. Established parameters. Tagged obstruction at 8069'. Opened
hydrostatic bailer w/ 60k down several times. Observed 20 bbls loss in trip tank. TOOH w/ hydrastatic bailer. Racked & LD hydrostatic bailer assy. No recovery in bailer. Damage noted on shoe - 2 gouges approximately 9" apart & 1-1/2" deep. Lost 2.5 bbls to hole f/ trip tank while tripping. Boosted riser w/ 15.7 ppg SBM. Flushed choke & kill lines w/ 15.7 ppg SBM. MU & TIH w/ BOP jet assy on 6-5/8" 34 ppf DP to 4942'. Observed 5 bbls gain on trip tank. Jetted BOPs w/ 15.7 ppg SBM. Boost riser w/ 15.7 ppg. TIH w/ BOP jet assy f/ 4942' to 5161'. Located upper annular. Function tested BOPs on 6-5/8" 34 ppf DP f/ bridge control panel; yellow pod; SEM A. Pumped 60 bbls of 17.7 ppg SBM slug. TOOH w/ jet assy f/ 5161' to 4350'. Functioned upper & lower blind shear rams & casing shear ram f/ driller's control panel; blue pod; SEM A. Functioned diverter f/ driller's control panel. TOOH w/ jet assy f/ 4350' to 2441'. 

6/20/15 - Cont'd to TOOH w/ jetting assy. Monitored well on trip tank. Well took 13.5 bbls for trip. RIH w/ 14.5" concave mill assy to 8070'. Tagged obstruction w/ 10k lbs down. Monitored well on trip tank. Well took proper displacement. Established parameters & milled on obstruction w/ 15.7 ppg SBM. Worked mill through obstruction at 8045' - 8070'. Flow checked on trip tank w/ no gain/loss observed. Pumped 60 bbl 17.7 ppg SBM slug. POOH w/ 14.5" concave milling assy. Flow checked well below BOP; no gain/loss observed. Lost total of 15 bbls on trip out of hole. Concave mill was
full gauge w/ a 2-1/8" circle worn in the center of the bottom of the mill. The string mill was 1/4" undergauge at very bottom of the bottom tapered section. There was 41.5 lbs of metal recovered on the magnets (351 lbs total since first magnet run). Monitored well on trip tank no gain/loss observed. ","WAR_START_DT":"2015-06-14","WELL_NAME":"  003"},{"   ":56,"API12":608074031500,"TEXT_REMARK":"6/21/15 - MU 12-1/4" taper mill assy & TIH to 8013'. Monitored well on trip tank. Total of 8 bbls lost during trip. TIH w/ 8-7/16" taper mill assy to 8069'. Total of 7.8 bbls gained during trip. Mill on obstruction at 8070'. 

6/22/15 - Cont'd to mill on obstruction at 8070' w/ 15.7 ppg SBM. Flow checked well on trip tank. Well static. Pumped 40 bbls of 17.7 ppg SBM slug. TOOH w/ 8.447" taper mill assy. Total losses of 10 bbls for trip. Monitored well on trip tank. Well static. PU 9-5/8" taper mill assy & TIH to 8069'. Milled on obstruction. Flow checked well on trip tank. Well static. Pumped 60 bbl of 17.7 ppg SBM. TOOH w/ 9-5/8" taper mill BHA. Cutrite worn off first 3-1/2" of mill. Nose of mill worn down to 3.80" OD.

SBM. Switch to rig pumps & displace w/ 3368 bbls of 15.6 ppg SBM. Bump plugs w/ 2000 psi (500 psi over final circulating rate). Cement in place at 16:30 hrs. Check floats (floats holding). TOC in annulus at 19100'. Close MPR & set seal assy w/ 10000 psi. Displace nerf ball down 6-5/8" landing string using 15.6 ppg SBM. Pump 30 bbl 17.5 ppg slug & chase. POOH w/ 6-5/8" landing string f/ 4788' to 296'.

8/6/15 - POOH w/ 6-5/8" landing string to surface. TIH w/ Dril-Quip selectable wear sleeve & set in wellhead. Flow check well on trip tank; static. Pump 40 bbls of 17.0 ppg slug & chase w/ 15.6 ppg SBM. POOH w/ Dril-Quip wear sleeve adapter. TIH w/ 12-1/4" x 14" BHA to 4381'. Slip & cut 98' of 2-1/8" drill line. Function test BSRs & CSR using bridge panel on yellow pod SEM A. Line up Halliburton unit on kill line & close upper BSR using driller's panel on blue pod SEM A. Test 14" casing to 250 psi for 5 min then 7040 psi for 30 min using 15.6 ppg SBM; good test. Pressure test lower BSR to 250 / 7040 psi for 5 min using 15.6 ppg SBM; good test. 

8/7/15 - TIH w/ 12-1/4" x 14" drilling assy f/ 4381' to 13863' filling w/ 15.6 ppg SBM. Function test diverter f/ driller's control panel. MU BOP test assy. RU chicksan lines & test hose. Locate upper annular & space out across BOPs. Test BOPs & related equipment on 6-5/8" drill pipe. Test performed f/ driller's panel on blue pod SEM A using IPT reference & Halliburton chart. Tested rams & fail safe valves to 250 / 11100 psi; annulars to 250 / 3600 psi and kelly hose to 250 / 7000 psi for 5 min. Function test BOPs on 6-5/8" drill pipe using bridge control panel on yellow pod SEM A. RD BOP test assy & surface equipment. TIH f/ 13863' to 15442'. 

8/8/15 - TIH w/ drilling assy f/ 15442' to 25219' filling w/ 15.6 ppg SBM. Wash down using 15.6 ppg SBM & tag TOC at 25856'. Obtain SCRs w/ 15.6 ppg SBM. Drill firm cement in 14" casing f/ 25856' to 25968'. ","WAR_START_DT":"2015-08-02","WELL_NAME":"  003"},{"   ":63,"API12":608074031500,"TEXT_REMARK":"8/9/15 - Cont'd to drill firm cement in 14" casing f/ 25968' to shoe at 26082'. Boost riser. W&R rathole hole f/ 26082' to 26290'. Boost riser. Drilled 10' of new formation to 26300'. Circ well to a consistent 15.6 ppg MW. Flow check well on trip tank; static. Pull 12-1/4" x 14" drilling BHA into shoe & prepare for FIT. Break circ down kill line & drill string. Close upper annular & verify space out. Perform FIT w/ 15.6 ppg SBM at 26082' TVD shoe depth to 1360 psi (16.60 ppg EMW). TIH & place reamer blades below 14" shoe. Drop 1-3/4" NOV reamer activation ball & pump down w/ 600 gpm at 3600 psi. Observe 130 psi decrease in pump pressure & 285 psi decrease in MWD turbine speed. Pull test against shoe & confirm reamer is open w/ 10k overpull. Wash down to 26300'. Take SCRs at 26294' w/ 15.6 ppg SBM. Drill ahead w/ 12-1/4" x 14" assy f/ 26300' to 26434'.

8/10/15 - Drill ahead f/ 26434' to 27065'. Flow check drilling breaks at 26554'; 26664' & 26958'; static. Circ 15.6 ppg SBM on bottom. Flow check well; static. Short trip into shoe & cont'd circulating 15.6 ppg SBM while boosting riser. TIH to 26900' & circ 15.6 ppg SBM while boosting riser. Drill ahead w/ drilling assy f/ 27065' to 27250'. 

8/11/15 - Drill ahead w/ drilling assy f/ 27250' to 27862'. After making connection at 27862'; noted significant pressure loss on standpipe. Found LCM packed off in suction & discharge strainers on #1 & #2 mud pumps. Changed pump line up & began offline cleaning of pump strainers. Hole monitored on trip tank (static) while troubleshooting pump issue. Drilled to 27898' using 15.6 ppg SBM. Lost boost pump & one mud pump due to LCM packoff in suction line. Stopped drilling & worked pipe while cleaning strainers in pump room & changing shaker screens. Monitor well on trip tank; static. Two mud pumps brought online. Established circulation & washed drill string back to bottom w/ occasional stall & losses noted at 27880'. Pulled up & reestablished flow. Attempt to work past 27886'. Pulled back to connection height & simulated connection on trip tank (observed 22 bbl gain in trip tank). Shut in well on lower annular & monitored pressures (SICP 527 psi / SIDPP 377 psi). Bled back 5.2 bbls & observe decrease in pressures (SICP 215 psi / SIDPP 318 psi). Pressures increased to initial shut in values after 40 min. Bump open float in drill string (SICP 596 psi / SIDPP 538 psi). Bled SICP to 0 psi w/ 15 bbls & shut in well (SICP 0 psi / SIDPP 117 psi). SICP increased 10 psi every 2-3 min & was 146 psi at report time.

8/12/15 - Cont'd recording pressures while monitoring well on trip tank (no gains/losses observed). Shut in pressures stabilized (SICP 596 psi / SIDPP 408 psi). Open choke & bled back 15 bbls (SICP 186 psi / SIDPP 127 psi). Closed choke & monitored pressure increase (SICP 601 psi). Using driller's method; circ 15.6 ppg SBM. After 273 bbls pumped; observed mud weight decrease to 14.9 ppg. Max gas observed 130 units. Shut in well & monitor pressures (SICP 400 psi / SIDPP 370 psi). Begin weight up of active system to 15.9 ppg KWM. Begin second circ of driller's method using 15.9 ppg KWM following step down chart. Stage pumps down due to possible plug/restriction. Monitor pressures (SICP 230 psi / SIDPP 107 psi). Flush through surface equipment w/ 15.9 ppg SBM to clear any obstructions. Stage pumps up to 40 spm while maintaining casing pressure at 230 psi & 1200 psi on drill pipe. Pressures indicating restriction in lines. Calculate new circulating pressures w/ reduced pump speeds & slow pump down to 30 spm while maintaining 800 psi on drill pipe. Bring pump down while maintaining 210 psi on casing & shut in well (SICP 210 psi / SIDPP 167 psi). Locate upper annular. Reduce closing pressure on UPR & close rams. Pump down kill side & up choke line. 

8/13/15 - Flushed BOP down kill line & up choke line w/ 15.6 ppg SBM w/ upper annular & upper pipe rams closed. Equalized pressure in BOP in preparation to open the upper pipe rams. Applied 20 psi on back side & opened upper pipe rams. SIDPP: 297 psi; SICP#1-236 psi; SICP#2-190 psi. Pumped 15.9 ppg KMW & cont'd w/ 2nd circ. DPP: 960 psi; CP#1: 16 psi; CP#2: 189 psi; 90% open choke. Drill pipe pressure increased f/ 960 to 1020 psi. Shut well in & changed mud pump line up to complete circulation. SIDPP: 350 psi; SICP#1: 265 psi; SICP#2: 310 psi. Bled off & monitored SPP: 126-293 psi. Pumped at 25 spm; SPP increased f/ 225-815 psi. Observed drop of SPP to 372 psi due to mud pump pack off. Shut well in & monitor pressures. SPP: 0 psi; SICP#1: 215 psi; SICP#2: 270 psi. Flushed mud pumps 2-5 through boost line w/ 15.9 ppg SBM. Pumped at 35 spm; SPP: 1150 psi; CP#1: 85 psi; CP#2: 270 psi w/ 15.9 ppg SBM. Shut in well & check float. SPP: 0 psi; SICP#1: 360 psi; SICP#2: 320 psi. Dropped 2.5" Well Commander activation ball & pumped down w/ 15.9 ppg SBM at 35 spm/1150 psi. Reduced pump speed to 16 spm/700 psi. No indication was observed that ball was on seat. Dropped 2nd 2.5" Well Commander activation ball & pumped down w/ 15.9 ppg SBM at 16 spm/700 psi. CP#1: 87 psi; CP#2: 174 psi. Ball on seat at 125 bbls pumped. Applied add'l 1100 psi over circulating pressure to verify ball on seat. Pumped 15.9 ppg KWM taking returns up the choke & kill lines w/ 16 spm/690 psi. Increased rate to 26 spm/830 psi. Monitored well on active gain/loss. Monitored riser on trip tank. Shut in well due to temporary loss of thrusters during thruster maintenance. Investigate cause of thruster power loss. Dropped 3rd Well Commander activation ball & began pumping down at 16 spm/700 psi taking returns up choke & kill. Slowed pump to 5 spm & Well Commander sheared at 1821 psi - now in closed position. Brought pump back up to 16 spm/630 psi. No change in circulating pressure. At 19:30; started displacing riser w/ 15.9 ppg KWM. Shut well in. Monitored & recorded pressures after riser full of 15.9 ppg SBM. SIDPP: 50 psi at 00:00 hrs.

***BSEE AND USCG WERE IMMEDIATELY NOTIFIED OF DP THRUSTER INCIDENT 8/13/15***

8/14/15 - Confirmed string was free by working string up & down. Boosted riser w/ 15.6 ppg SBM. Monitored pressures SIDPP: 0 psi; CP#1: 126 psi; CP#2: 129 psi. Worked string f/ 27864' to 27844'. Shut well in SIDPP: 187 psi; CP#1: 156 psi; CP#2: 170 psi. Flushed BOP down choke & kill lines w/ closed upper pipe rams w/ 15.9 ppg KWM. DP pressure increased to 448 psi. Bled off DPP to 0 psi & monitored. Increased to 157 psi. Opened upper pipe ram & monitored pressures DPP: 217 psi; CP#1: 116 psi; CP#2: 0
psi. Monitored well on choke line; static. Opened kill line & monitored both lines on trip tank for 30 min. 30 psi increase on DPP: 247 psi. Bled off DPP to 0 psi. Shut well in & monitored pressure. DPP: 157 psi; CP#1: 136 psi; CP#2: 79 psi. Closed upper pipe rams. Flushed BOP w/ 15.9 ppg KWM. Flow checked well on trip tanks. Shut well in & monitored pressure. SIDPP: 207 psi; CP#1: 85 psi; CP#2: 39 psi. Weighted up active to 16.5 ppg for riser cap. Monitored casing & DP pressures. Monitored riser on trip tank. Displaced w/ 16.5 ppg SBM f/ above MPR to top of riser through choke & kill. Closed upper annular & swept BOP stack pumping down kill line taking returns up choke line w/ 16.5 ppg SBM. No gas noted in returns. SIDPP: 210 psi. Flow checked well w/ MPR closed & annular open; static 15 min. Opened MPR & annular & flow checked on open well; static 45 min. Still had SIDPP: 210 psi. Located on lower annular. Function tested BOP f/ blue pod SEM A f/ bridge panel. Function tested f/ yellow pod SEM A f/ driller's panel. Unable to perform diverter function test due to on going well control
operations. Monitored well on trip tank; static. Pumped 150 bbls of 16.5 ppg SBM down DP. No returns while pumping. SPP fell f/ 888 psi to 450 psi. SIDPP: 0 psi after
pumping 16.5 ppg SBM into string. Flow checked well on trip tank prior to pumping OOH. Well static. Pumped OOH f/ 27864' to 27600'. Pumped steel displacement + DP capacity (6 bbls per stand). Monitored well on trip tank.

8/15/15 - Pumped OOH f/ 27600' to 26922'. Pumped closed ended displacement for every stand w/ 16.5 ppg SBM. Worked through tight spots @ 27405' and 27264'. TIH f/ 26542' to 26922'. Installed TIW & DP single on top of string. Spaced out & closed in on upper annular. Boosted riser w/ 16.5 ppg SBM. Opened upper annular. Flow checked well for 15 min on trip tank. Well static. Pumped OOH f/ 26922' to 26012'. Pumped closed ended displacement w/ 15.9 ppg SBM. Flow checked well on trip tank; static. RD 12' drilling bails & BX-7 elevators. RU 16' bails & BX-7 elevators. Monitored well on trip tank; static. RU OES fill-up tool. Pumped OOH using OES flowback tool f/ 26012' to 23101'. Filled hole w/ 15.9 ppg SBM. Flow checked well at 23101'; static. Closed upper annular & filled riser w/ 16.5 ppg SBM. Monitored riser on active gain/loss. Monitored well below annular through fail safe - no pressure buildup. Opened annular & flow checked well; static. Attempted to perform diverter function test but could not get mud level to drop below housing. Unable to complete test.","WAR_START_DT":"2015-08-09","WELL_NAME":"  003"},{"   ":64,"API12":608074031500,"TEXT_REMARK":"8/16/15 - Pumped OOH f/ 23101' to 22571' pumping steel displacement of 15.9 ppg SBM down DP. Flow checked well on trip tanks. Observed 5 bbls increase over 50 min period. Installed FOSV & spaced out. Shut well in on upper annular. Closed upper pipe rams & displaced choke line w/ 15.9 ppg SBM. Opened upper pipe rams & monitored pressure on choke line. Opened upper annular & flow checked well for 15 min; static. Pumped OOH f/ 22571' to 22307' pumping closed end displacement of 15.9 ppg SBM down DP. Changed out OES control panel. Monitored well on trip tanks; static. Pumped OOH f/ 22307' to 19663' pumping steel displacement of 15.9 ppg SBM every 3 stands. TOOH f/ 19663' to 19001' filling hole w/ steel displacement of 15.9 ppg SBM every 3 stands. Flow checked well; static. Spaced out; closed upper annular and filled riser with 16.5 ppg SBM @ 135 spm/ 2;950 psi. Monitored well - static. Opened upper annular. Flow checked well; static. TOOH f/ 19001' to 18208'. Proper fill on trip tank. At 18208'; discovered the top aluminum clamp f/ WWT non-rotating protector was missing. Removed lower clamp & non-rotating protector f/ pipe. Monitored well on trip tank; static. TOOH f/ 18208' to 16363'. Proper fill on trip tank. 

8/17/15 - TOOH f/ 16363' to 14257'. Function tested diverter f/ bridge control panel. Conditioned riser cap w/ 16.5 ppg SBM. TOOH to 8862'. Spotted 100 bbls of 15.9 ppg SBM in riser. Pumped 16.5 ppg SBM out of trip tanks & filled w/ 15.9 ppg SBM. TOOH to 3060'. Spotted 50 bbls of 15.9 ppg SBM in riser.

8/18/15 - Pumped 50 bbl of 15.9 ppg SBM down boost line. TOOH to RKB; racking BHA in derrick. Spotted 50 bbls of 16.5 ppg SBM in riser. Hung off block. Slip & cut 155' of drill line. Received approval f/ Beau Boudreaux to RIH w/ cmt diverter. MU & TIH w/ cmt diverter assy to 1338'. Circ'd 15.9 ppg SBM. Boosted riser w/ 15.9 ppg SBM. TIH f/ 7695' to 10700'. Displaced riser w/ 15.9 ppg SBM. 

8/19/15 - TIH to 26270'. Displaced riser w/ 15.9 ppg SBM. Displaced choke line w/ 15.9 ppg SBM. Closed upper annular & cont'd boosting riser w/ upper pipe rams closed. Opened upper annular & cont'd boosting w/ upper pipe rams closed. Closed upper annular & opened upper pipe rams while boosting riser.

8/20/15 - Pumped 16.5 ppg SBM down kill line. Pumped 96 bbls of 6.67 ppg base oil down kill line. Circ'd 15.9 ppg SBM down drill string; staging pumps up f/ 20 spm to 45 spm. Shut in well on upper annular. Began monitoring pressures. Closed upper pipe rams. Displaced base oil & 16.5 ppg mud f/ choke & kill lines w/ 15.9 ppg SOBM. Monitored pressures. Opened pipe rams. Circ'd 15.9 ppg SBM down drill string taking returns up choke. Boosted riser w/ 15.9 ppg SBM. Closed upper pipe rams. Flow checked well. Put a 16.8 ppg SBM riser cap in 100 bbl increments. Pumped total of 1550 bbls. Beau Boudreaux of BSEE Lafayette granted a 48 hour blind shear ram function test extension - due Saturday; August 22nd at midnight. Monitored pressures. Circ'd riser w/ boost pump w/ 16.8 ppg mud.

8/21/15 - Boosted riser w/ 16.8 ppg SBM. Pumped 870 bbls of 17.5 ppg SBM through boost line as riser cap. Filled riser below cap w/ 15.9 ppg SBM. Monitored well below upper pipe rams on trip tank for 15 min; static. Opened rams & flow checked well; static. Bled pressure off DP. Pumped 17.5 ppg SBM down DP in 10 bbl increments to balance DP; taking returns up choke line. Flow checked well; static. Pumped a total of 109 bbls of 17.5 ppg mud into DP. Pumped 10 bbls of 15.9 ppg SBM on top of 17.5 ppg SBM. Opened upper pipe rams & monitored well on trip tank; static. TIH f/ 26252' to 26358'. Located tool joint on upper annular & performed BOP function test f/ driller's control panel; blue pod; SEM A. TOOH f/ 26358' to 24382'. Located on upper annular. Closed upper pipe rams & boosted riser w/ 15.9 ppg SBM. Opened upper pipe rams & flow checked well on trip tank; static. TOOH f/ 24382' to 20979'. Received RPD approval f/ Beau Boudreaux for the revised suspension plan.

8/22/15 - TOOH f/ 20979' to 17674'. Monitor well on trip tank. TIH f/ 17674' to 18203' w/ bare 6-5/8" DP. Located on upper annular & closed upper pipe rams. Boosted riser w/ 15.9 ppg SBM until 17.5 ppg SBM at top of riser. TIH f/ 18203' to 20716'. Installed FOSV. Locate on upper annular & closed in on upper pipe ram. Built 17.5 ppg SBM to add to existing riser cap. Flushed kill line w/ 17.5 ppg SBM taking returns up choke line. Pumped 100 bbls of 17.5 ppg SBM into riser. Marty Rinaudo; BSEE Lafayette granted an extension for the blind shear ram function test until Monday August 24 at midnight. An extension for the SSBOP test was also granted until after the slip joint is repaired & the LMRP is relatched to the BOP. Pumped 84 bbls of 17.5 ppg SBM into riser. Opened upper pipe rams to monitor well on trip tank. TIH f/ 20716' to 25350'. Located on upper annular & closed well in on upper pipe rams. RU cmt stand & lines. Opened upper annular & monitored well on trip tank while building spacer for cmt job. ","WAR_START_DT":"2015-08-16","WELL_NAME":"  003"},{"   ":65,"API12":608074031500,"TEXT_REMARK":"8/23/15 - Broke circ w/ 10 bbls of tuned spacer III. Performed 7000 psi line test; good. Pumped 80 bbls of tuned spacer III. M&P 150 bbls / 591 sx / 842 cuft of 16.4 ppg slurry at 5.0 bpm. Pumped 30 bbls of tuned spacer III behind cement. Displaced cement w/ 500 bbls of 15.9 ppg SBM. Stopped pumping. Closed upper annular & completed cement displacement; bullheading cement w/ 249 bbls of 15.9 ppg SBM. Cement in place at 05:30 hrs. Cement plug f/ 25750' - 26612' (332'/49 bbls inside casing; 530'/101
bbls in open hole). RD cement stand & lines. Monitored well on trip tank; static. Stripped OOH f/ 25348' to 23365'; pumping closed end displacement below annular while pulling. Monitored well on trip tank. WOC. Halliburton performed 1000 psi pressure test to confirm plug in place. TIH f/ 23365' to 25745' to tag cement plug. No solid
cement tagged - stringers seen but would not hold 15k lbs. TOOH f/ 25745' to 24688'. Broke circ. 

8/24/15 - TOOH f/ 24688' to 23365'. Removed TIW & IBOP f/ string. Monitored well on trip tank; static. Circ 15.9 ppg SBM while WOC. TIH f/ 23365' to 25214'. Washed f/ 25214' to 25810'. Tagged hard cement at 25810' w/ 20k lbs down. Pumped 70 bbls of 17.9 ppg SBM slug. TOOH f/ 25810' to 23893'. Function tested diverter. TOOH f/ 23893' to 17674'. MU Blackhawk storm packer assy. TIH f/ 17674' to 23212' (bit depth) positioning packer at 5513'. Received approval f/ Marty Rinaudo; BSEE Lafayette; to hang off 17000' of DP below storm packer rather than 10 stands. Broke circulation before setting packer; Set packer at 5513'. Tested backside of storm packer w/ rig pumps to 1000 psi for 5 min. Good test. TOOH f/ 5513' to 4278'. Conducted BSR/CSR function test on driller's control panel; blue pod; SEM A. Pressure tested storm packer w/ rig pumps to 1000 psi. Pumped 132 bbls of base oil down drill string w/ Halliburton unit. Closed annular. Began bleeding back to Halliburton unit to perform
negative test on storm packer.

8/25/15 - Pumped 145 bbls of 6.67 ppg base oil down string. Closed annular & bled back 42 bbls of base oil to Halliburton unit. Pressured up w/ Haliburton unit to 2057 psi. Spaced out & closed UPR. Bled back 4.7 bbls to Haliburton unit; pressure dropped
to 0 psi. Recorded test on chart at Haliburton unit for 30 min. Good test. Displaced choke; kill & boost to 8.6 ppg SW. Displaced well by pumping base oil followed by Xan-Plex spacer followed by 8.6 ppg SW. Pumped two complete circulations & flushed mud pumps & surface equipment w/ drill water. Flow checked well; static. Spaced out in BOP to test annulars against test rams. Broke circ using mud pump down choke line & up riser. Tested upper & lower annulars to 3600 psi for 5 min each against test ram using 8.6 ppg SW w/ rig mud pump. Monitored riser on trip tank. Good test. Attempted to TOOH but fluid was U-tubing up string. Circ w/ 8.6 ppg SW. Boosted riser. TOOH f/ 5350' to RKB. Slipped & cut 169' of drill line. Tested casing against shear ram & storm packer to 250 / 1000 psi for 5 min each w/ SW. Good test. Engaged diverter running tool. Latched diverter to diverter running tool & pulled out of housing. PU riser landing joint.

8/26/15 - Hooked up ctrl lines to slip joint; latched & locked slip joint inner barrel. Unlatched LMRP. Moved rig to safe zone. Removed ctrl lines f/ slip joint. Leveled rig; locked RST ring into place. Unlatched slip joint f/ RST ring; removed storm loops. Laid out landing joint. Removed kelly hose f/ TDX 1250. With slip joint on spider; unlocked gator locks & scoped out inner barrel to inspect for wear. No wear found. Locked gator locks; removed upper packer on slip joint & replaced w/ new one. Performed 500 psi test. Test failed due to flat seal leaking. Removed & replaced lower packer seals & flat seal. Tested to 500 psi. Good test. Opened upper packer
seals & replaced flat seal. ROV installed new AX ring gasket on LMRP connector.

8/27/15 - Cont'd testing upper & lower slip joint seals to 500 psi for 5 min using
8.6 ppg SW. Changed kelly hose on main TDX. PU landing joint & torque to slip joint. Position slip joint in moonpool & attached storm loops. Lock RTS ring to slip joint & test w/ 50k overpull & 15k set down to verify latch. Take weight off RTS & unlatch f/
stow position. At 0830 hrs; begin rig move to NP 3 location 365' away. Note: At 0725 hrs; received clarification f/ Beau Boudreaux that the wellhead connector does not need to be re-tested since it was not unlatched f/ the wellhead. The LMRP connector & full BOP test will be performed upon relatch. Position rig over BOP & latch LMRP using driller's control panel on yellow pod SEM A. Verify latch w/ 100k overpull. ROV
verified positive latch on LMRP connector; C&K mini connectors & yellow/blue pod stingers. Attached control lines & hoses to slip joint. Unlock slip joint & scope out to rig floor. Break out & LD landing joint. RD manual riser running tools & RU BX7 elevators. PU diverter & replace seals in lock down dogs. Land diverter & extend lock downs. Confirm w/ 50k overpull. LD diverter running tool. RD remaining riser handling equipment. Install outer ring & master bushings in main rotary. MU Blackhawk 14" packer retrieval tool & TIH to 2822'. Function tested diverter on auto sequence. Pumped through port & starboard lines w/ 8.6 ppg SW. Tested C&K lines using 8.6 ppg SW. Test performed to 250/11100 psi for 5 min. Circ 8.6 ppg SW down kill line & up choke line prior to opening upper blind shear rams. TIH w/ retrieval tool f/ 2822' to 5206'. Locate tool joint on upper annular & space out for BOP testing.

8/28/15 - Attempt low pressure test on LMRP connector (no test). Spot 40 gal of dye down kill line (could not verify a leak w/ ROV). Troubleshoot by closing upper pipe rams & testing to 250 psi (good test). Open UPR & close upper annular. Increased closing pressure on LMRP connector by 500 psi. Pressure test connector to 250/4850 psi (good test). Test BOPs & related equipment on 6-5/8" drill pipe. Test performed w/ bridge panel on yellow pod SEM A using IPT reference & Halliburton chart. Tested rams & fail safe valves to 250/11100 psi & annulars to 250/3600 psi. Note: At 1350 hrs; received approval f/ David LeLeux to proceed w/ operations on NP 3. RD surface test equipment while continuing offline testing of BOPs. TIH on 6-5/8" drill pipe f/ 5204' to 5469' (44' above storm packer). Cont'd testing BOPs on 6-5/8" drill pipe. Test performed w/ bridge panel on yellow pod SEM A using IPT reference & Halliburton chart. Tested fail safe valves to 250/11100 psi & kelly hose to 250/7000 psi. Switch f/ yellow pod SEM A to blue pod SEM A & observed increasing gallon count on flow meter. Locate on upper annular. Troubleshoot gallon count issue w/ blue pod.

8/29/15 - Cont'd troubleshooting flow meter gallon count issue on blue pod. Pulled drill string to 4411' (~500"'above BOPs). ROV encountered leak on bue pod stinger. Functioned POD & observed debris fall f/ stinger. Latch blue pod stinger w/ correct
gallon count on flow meter. Verified latch w/ ROV. TIH f/ 4411' to 5450' & spaceout on upper annular. Function test BOPs on 6-5/8" drill pipe using driller's panel on blue pod SEM A. Function test diverter f/ driller's control panel. Displaced well f/ 8.6 ppg SW to 15.9 ppg SBM. TIH f/ 5450' to top of 14" Blackhawk storm packer at 5513'. Latch packer & confirm w/ 50k overpull. Slackoff to neutral & open storm valve. Close lower annular & release packer. Circ 310 bbls of 15.9 ppg down drill string & up C&K lines. Flow check well on trip tank w/ closed annular (static). Open annular & monitor well on trip tank for 15 min (static). Pump 65 bbl slug of 17.9 ppg. POOH f/ 23213' to 6621'. Flow check well prior to pulling BHA through BOPs (static). Cont'd POOH to 1337'.","WAR_START_DT":"2015-08-23","WELL_NAME":"  003"},{"   ":66,"API12":608074031500,"TEXT_REMARK":"8/30/15 - POOH w/ cmt assy. TIH w/ 12-1/4" x 14" BHA to 4386'. Slip & cut 61' of drill line. Line up Halliburton unit on kill line & close upper BSR using bridge panel on yellow POD SEM A. Test 14" casing to 250 psi for 5 min then 6635 psi for 30 min using 15.9 ppg SBM. Test lower BSR to 250/6395 psi for 5 min. Function test BSRs & CSR using bridge panel on yellow POD SEM A. TIH w/ drilling assy f/ 4386' to 24694'.

8/31/15 - Cont'd TIH w/ drilling assy f/ 24694' to 25752'. Wash down & tag TOC at 25791' w/ 20k down. Drill cement f/ 25791' to 26265' while boosting riser. Drop 1-3/4" reamer activation ball. Did not observe change in standpipe pressure or turbine speed on MWD. Stop pumping & pulled reamer 20' into 14" shoe. No sign of overpull entering shoe or inside casing observed. Slack off & place reamer 20' outside of shoe. Attempt pull test against shoe w/ no overpull or drag observed. Slack off reamer 20' below shoe & shut down pumps. Stage pumps up to 425 gpm at 2885 psi & observe no change in standpipe pressure or turbine speed. Cont'd attempts to open reamer while drilling cement f/ 26265' to 26294' while boosting riser. Stop pumps. Bring pumps back online & pull reamer to within 20' of shoe. Shut down pumps for 5 min. Bring pumps back online & attempt to pull test reamer against shoe. No overpull observed. Received a 24 hr extension on the BOP test f/ Michael LaFleur. Performed squeeze operations w/ 46 bbls of 15.9 ppg SOBM. Squeezed at 1.1 bpm reducing to 0.3 bpm. Squeeze pressure ranged f/ 725 psi to 539 psi. Shut in on DP & squeezed backside w/ 10 bbls down the choke line. WOC. Function tested BOP f/ driller's panel; yellow pod & bridge panel; blue pod. Washed down w/ cement stinger f/ 27228' to 27310'. Tagged cement w/ 20k lbs at 27310'. Attempted to wash down further; no success. Circ'd foam ball while displacing well to 15.7 ppg SOBM. Pumped 85 bbls 17.9 ppg slug. Flow checked well on trip tank; static. TOOH w/ 5" cement stinger f/ 27310' to 19559'.  Note: Offline testing of choke manifold & failsafe valves began at 23:30 hrs.

11/11/16 - POOH w/ 5" cement diverter f/ 19559' to 13228'. Note: Offline testing choke manifold to 250 / 9000 psi w/ 15.7 ppg SOBM. MU BOP test assy. Space out in BOP. RU test lines to double dutch. Test BOPs on 5" DP w/ 15.7 ppg SOBM f/ bridge panel; Blue pod; SEM B. All pipe rams; failsafe valves; TDS valves; FOSV & choke manifold valves tested to 250 / 11700 psi for 5 min each. Annulars & failsafe bleed valves tested to 250 / 3500 psi for 5 min each. All buffer manifold valves tested to 250 / 9000 psi for 5 min each. All tests good. RD test lines & double dutch. MU BOP test plug & Nutec hang off tool & TIH f/ 13228' to 17825'. Landed test plug at 4634' & closed upper annular on 6-5/8" DP. Performed verfication test to 1000 psi using rig pump down drill string w/ 15.7 ppg SOBM. Good test. Opened annular. Backed off hang off tool. Pulled above BOP to 4509'. Tested BSR to 250 / 11700 psi for 5 min each w/ 15.7 ppg SOBM f/ driller's panel; yellow pod; SEM B.

11/12/16 - Function tested upper; lower & casing BSR f/ driller panel; Yellow pod; SEM B & bridge panel; Blue pod; SEM B. Pumped 100 bbl slug. TOOH f/ 17825' to 13248'. B/O hang off tool & BOP test plug. Located on upper annular & closed test ram. Test BOPs on 5" DP w/ 15.7 ppg SOBM f/ bridge panel; Blue pod; SEM B. All pipe rams; failsafe valves; TDS valves; FOSV & choke manifold valves tested to 250 / 11700 psi for 5 min each. Annulars & failsafe bleed valves tested to 250 / 3500 psi for 5 min each. All buffer manifold valves tested to 250 / 9000 psi for 5 min each. All tests good. Function tested BOP f/ driller panel; Yellow pod; SEM B. Performed diverter function test f/ driller panel. Pumped 100 bbls slug. TOOH w/ 5" cement stinger f/ 13228' to surface. Note: Offline performed casing test against LBSR to 6000 psi using 15.7 ppg SOBM. Good test. MU & RIH w/ 11-7/8" casing & float collar jt to 1551'. ","WAR_START_DT":"2016-11-06","WELL_NAME":"  004"},{"   ":108,"API12":608074032000,"TEXT_REMARK":"11/13/16 - RIH w/ 11-7/8" casing f/ 1551' to 3106'. MU 14" x 11-7/8" VersaFlex hanger f/ 3106' to 3131'. TIH w/ 11-7/8" liner on DP f/ 3131' to 20511'. Compensated while running hanger through BOP. Began to lose string weight & hydraulically lift while RIH at 20511'. Worked string f/ 20511' to 20708'. Had free movement up but weight would stack during slack off. String weight would slowly come back while sitting in one place. Slacked off to as much as 100k lbs. When stopped weight would come back. RD OES flow back tool. Attempted to circ. No excess torque seen on string. Observed 130k lbs lift on string w/ 1000 psi on standpipe. Stopped pumping & worked string up.
No returns seen.

11/14/16 - Pumped OOH f/ 20708' to 19914'. RU OES flow back tool. Pumped OOH w/ 11-7/8" casing f/ 19914' to 9733'. Note: Unable to circulate up annulus. Filling hole down DP w/ swept volume + steel displacement.

11/15/16 - Pumped OOH w/ 11-7/8" scab liner f/ 9733' to 3175' filling hole down DP w/ swept volume + steel displacement w/ 15.7 ppg SOBM. No circulation observed. Monitor well on trip tanks. Pull hanger through BOP. Stopped at 7331' and 7205' to attempt to circulate. Pressured up to 1900 psi & held for 10 min. Pressure bled down to 1700 psi. RD OES flowback tool; removed rig bushings; installed 11-7/8" casing slips; power frame tracks & associated equipment. Pumped 240 bbls of 17.5 ppg SOBM slug. Flow checked well on trip tank; static. B/O and L/D 11-7/8" x 14" Versaflex hanger. No damage or signs of blockage seen on hanger. Removed BX-5 elevators & installed 11-7/8" casing elevators. TOOH w/ 11-7/8" scab liner f/ 3106' to surface. No indications of damage or blockage on casing or seal assy. RD 11-7/8" casing equipment & RU DP handling gear. TIH w/ 14" casing scraper & polish mill assy f/ surface to 4056'. 

11/16/16 - Slip & cut 137' of drill line. TIH w/ 14" casing scraper BHA f/ 4056' to 20270'. Worked 14" casing scraper assy through casing f/ 20270' to 25604'. Tagged top of 11-7/8" liner hanger w/ polish mill assy w/ 20K lbs down at 25604'. Polished PBR. Back reamed OOH w/ 14" casing scraper assy f/ 25604' to 23972'. 

11/17/16 - Backreamed OOH w/ 14" casing scraper assy f/ 23792' to 20300'. CBU at 20300'. TOOH f/ 20300' to surface. RU 11-7/8" casing handling equipment. MU & run 11-7/8" to 3172'. PU 11-7/8" x 14" VersaFlex hanger & MU Blackhawk single plug to RT. Stabbed plug into casing stump & MU hanger to casing. RD casing equipment. TIH w/ 11-7/8" liner on 6-5/8" landing string f/ 3227' to 4548'.

11/18/16 - TIH w/ 11-7/8" liner f/ 4548' to 23636'. Liner stood up at 23636' w/ 100k lbs. Worked down to 23663'. Attempted to circ at 1 bpm & trapped 1500 psi (150k lbs of lift on string). Released pressure w/ bleed off & regained string weight. Able to slack off freely. TIH w/ 11-7/8" liner f/ 23663' to 25604'. Tagged TOL at 25604' w/ 50k lbs down. PU 10' above TOL. MU TDX & circ'd 15.7 ppg SOBM. 

11/19/16 - Circ'd 15.7 ppg SOBM. Dropped 2" float conversion ball. MU Blackhawk cmt head. RIH f/ 25550' to 25604'; landing in PBR w/ 50k lbs down on no-go. Tested seal assy to 500 psi. Good test. Unstung f/ PBR & noted pressure drop. Positioned seal assy 10' above PBR. RU cement line & circ'd 15.7 ppg SOBM. Broke circ w/ cmt unit w/ 10 bbls of 16.0 ppg Tuned Spacer III. Tested lines to 7000 psi. Good test. Pumped 50 bbls of 16.0 ppg Tuned Spacer III. M&P 120 bbls / 674 cuft / 621 sx (66 bbls mix fluid) of 16.4 ppg Class H slurry. Yield: 1.086 ft/sx. Dropped wiper dart. Pumped 25 bbls of 16.0 ppg Tuned Spacer III. Displaced cement w/ cmt unit w/ 870 bbls of 15.7 ppg SOBM. Launched plug at 569 bbls w/ 4300 psi. Did not bump plug. Cement in place at 13:30 hrs. ETOC - 22417'. Dropped 2.75" VersaFlex setting ball & allowed to fall on seat. Lowered string to sting seal assy into PBR & slacked off 90k lbs on No-go. Cement unit bled off 5 bbls & verified seal assy was holding. Performed line test to 7000 psi. Good test. Set VersaFlex hanger. Released f/ liner hanger. Estimated TOL at 22417'. Broke out cement head & MU single with wiper ball installed & circ'd 2 btms up f/ 22417'. Functioned diverter Port side f/ BCP. Performed BOP function test f/ bridge panel; yellow pod; & driller's panel; blue pod. Performed 10 min flow check on trip tank; static. Pumped 75 bbls of 17.5 ppg slug. TOOH w/ VersaFlex RT f/ 22417' to 21406'.","WAR_START_DT":"2016-11-13","WELL_NAME":"  004"},{"   ":109,"API12":608074032000,"TEXT_REMARK":"11/20/16 - TOOH w/ VersaFlex RT f/ 21406' to surface. TIH w/ 10-5/8" cement clean out assy f/ surface to 4216'. Slipped & cut 145' of drill line. TIH f/ 4216' to 20053'.

11/21/16 - TIH w/ 10-5/8" clean out assy f/ 20053' to 22962'. Washed in hole f/ 22962' to 25247'. Tagged cement at 25247' w/ 20k lbs. Drilled cement f/ 25247' to 25740'. Drilled float collar f/ 25386' to 25389'. Washed down f/ 25740' to 27198'. Drilled cement f/ 27198' to 27443'. W&R cement f/ 27443' to 28600'. Circ'd cement above WH f/ 28600' w/ 15.7 ppg SBM. Spaced out in BOP & closed upper annular. Performed casing test to 1500 psi for 30 min. Good test. W&R cement f/ 28600' to 29330'. 

11/22/16 - Drilled cement w/ 10-5/8" clean out assy f/ 29330' to 29380'. Pumped OOH f/ 29380' to 29200'. Pumped up MWD ESD = 15.88 ppg. Performed FIT w/ cement unit using 15.7 ppg SOBM to 16.3 ppg EMW at 29200' shoe depth. MWD FIT value = 16.6 ppg (25146 psi at 29171' sensor depth). TOOH wet f/ 29200' to 28912'. TOOH f/ 28912' to surface. RU wireline for CBL run.

11/23/16 - RIH w/ wireline; CBL tool. Logged casing w/ CBL tool f/ 29200' to 28828' where tool failed. POOH & RD wireline. TIH making up 10-5/8" x 12-1/4" drilling BHA f/ surface to 960'. Shallow tested MWD w/ 350 gpm / 600 psi; good test. Loaded radioactive sources. Note: Offline tested BOP failsafe valves & choke / kill manifold w/ 15.7 ppg SOBM f/ driller's panel; yellow pod. All failsafe & choke / kill valves tested to 250 / 11700 psi for 5 min each. All buffer valves tested to 250 / 9000 psi for 5 min each. TIH w/ 10-5/8" x 12-1/4" drilling BHA f/ 960' to 7247'. RU double dutch test assy & steel lines for BOP testing. Tested BOPs & related equipment w/ 15.7 ppg SOBM f/ driller's panel; yellow pod. Failsafe valves; pipe rams & choke manifold valves tested to 250 / 11700 psi for 5 min each. All buffer manifold valves tested to 250 / 9000 psi for 5 min each. Annulars tested to 250 / 3500 psi for 5 min
each. All tests good. 

11/24/16 - Test BOPs & related equipment on 5" drill pipe w/ 15.7 ppg SBM. Tests performed f/ driller's panel on yellow POD SEM "B". Tested pipe rams to 250 / 11700 psi; annulars to 250 / 3500 psi & buffer manifold valves to 250 / 9000 psi for 5 min each. Function test BOPs on 5" drill pipe using bridge panel on blue POD SEM "B" & driller's panel on yellow POD SEM "B". Function diverter auto sequence f/ bridge panel on STRB side. TIH w/ 10-5/8" x 12-1/4" drilling assy f/ 7247' to 29188'. Wash to bottom f/ 29188' to 29380'. Drill 10-5/8" hole f/ 29380' to 29409'. Drop 1-3/4" reamer activation ball. 

11/25/16 - Circ 1-3/4" reamer activation ball. Pull test reamer against 11-7/8" casing shoe w/ 10k overpull & confirm reamer open. Drill 10-5/8" x 12-1/4" directional hole f/ 29409' to 30070'. 

11/26/16 - Drill 10-5/8" x 12-1/4" directional hole f/ 30070' to 30840'.","WAR_START_DT":"2016-11-20","WELL_NAME":"  004"},{"   ":110,"API12":608074032000,"TEXT_REMARK":"11/27/16 - Drill 10-5/8" x 12-1/4" directional hole f/ 30840' to 31568' w/ 15.7 ppg SBM. Note: At 13:57 hrs; received approval f/ Mark Malbrue to revise 9-5/8" section TD to previously approved depth of 31870' TVD.

11/28/16 - Drill 10-5/8" x 12-1/4" directional hole f/ 31568' to 31826' w/ 15.7 ppg SBM. Perform stretch calculation log w/ MWD. Take formation pressure of 15.95 ppg EMW w/ TesTrak probe depth at 31702' MD (31530' TVD). Drill 10-5/8" x 12-1/4" directional hole f/ 31826' to 31983'. Work drill string multiple times through bad spot f/ 31965' to 31983'. Note: At 14:20 hrs; received approval f/ Marty Rinaudo to continue drilling operations to 32400' TVD. Drill 10-5/8" x 12-1/4" directional hole f/ 31983' to 32190'. 

11/29/16 - Drill 10-5/8" x 12-1/4" directional hole f/ 32190' to 32210'. Circ cutting samples up f/ 32210'. Drill 10-5/8" x 12-1/4" directional hole f/ 32210' to section TD at 32230'. Displace well to 15.9 ppg. Pump OOH f/ 32230' to 31904'. Attempt 12 TesTrak formation pressures f/ 31904' to 31652' (bit depth). Obtain 2 successful pressures at the following probe depths:
31637' MD (31474' TVD) - 15.88 ppg EMW
31560' MD (31407' TVD) - 15.88 ppg EMW
Pump OOH f/ 31652' to 31568'.

11/30/16 - Pump OOH f/ 31568' to 11-7/8" TOL. POOH wet f/ 21388' to 20980'. Pump 75 bbl slug of 17.9 ppg & chase w/ 15.9 ppg SBM. Function test BOPs on 6-5/8" drill pipe using bridge panel on yellow POD SEM "B" & driller's panel on blue POD SEM "B". Function diverter auto sequence f/ bridge PORT line. POOH f/ 20980' to 3986'. Slip & cut 215' of drill line. POOH f/ 3986' to 1594'.

12/1/16 - POOH f/ 1594' to surface. Offline function test upper & lower BSRs & CSR f/ driller's panel on Blue POD SEM "B" & bridge panel on Yellow POD SEM "B". RU wireline equipment. MU logging assy #1 (OMRI-AST) & surface test equipment. RIH w/ wireline assy f/ surface to 11-7/8" shoe at 29200'. Log down w/ AST f/ shoe to 31230'. Made multiple attempts w/ increasing resistance to pass through tar stringers w/ no success. Attempt to open tool arms & log up w/ OMRI (motor stalling). Decision made to
POOH w/ wireline & replace dipmeter. POOH w/ wireline assy #1 f/ 31230' to surface & LD same. PU backup tool & MU wireline assy #2 (OMRI). RIH to 31230'. Open arms on OMRI dipmeter & begin logging open hole up f/ 31230'. 

12/2/16 - Log f/ 31230' to 11-7/8" shoe at 29200'. POOH. LD OMRI logging assy & RD wireline equipment. RU for 9-5/8" casing operations. MU 9-5/8" shoe track (Reamer Joint; 1 Stand & FC Joint). RIH w/ 9-5/8" casing to 4917'. MU 9-5/8" Versaflex hanger. Lower hanger assy through rotary & install XP-1000 slips & bushing. RD casing equipment. TIH w/ 9-5/8" casing to 22135'.

12/3/16 - TIH w/ 9-5/8" casing f/ 22135' to 30059'. Convert Blackhawk float collar w/ 4 bbl/min at 660 psi. W&R liner down w/ partial returns f/ 30059' to 32110'. Observed various tight spots f/ 31254' to 32110' setting depth.
Note: 9-5/8" Liner Depths
9-5/8" TOL - 27161'
9-5/8" FC - 31929'
9-5/8" Shoe - 32110'
RU cement lines. Pump 10 bbls of 16.3 ppg Tuned Spacer & test lines to 8500 psi. Pump add'l 90 bbls of 16.3 ppg spacer at 5 bbls/min w/ 1760 psi & drop Blackhawk SSR bottom dart. M&P 100 bbls (561.4 ft3) of 16.7# Class H + Silica cement (408 sks / 50 bbl mix fluid). Yield 1.379 ft3/sk. Drop SSR top dart. Pump 25 bbls of 16.3 ppg spacer & 20 bbls of 15.9 ppg SBM at 5 bbl/min & 1745 psi. Switch to rig pumps & displace w/ 1041 bbls of 15.9 ppg SBM at 8 bbl/min w/ 1715 psi (Slowed to 6 bbl/min at 1300 psi & observed LWP #1 shear at 2650 psi & LWP #2 shear at 2590 psi). Cont'd displacement w/ 1220 psi observing no indication of either plug bumping. Pressure fell to 330 psi w/ pumps off. Cement in place at 15:48 hrs. Bled pressure f/ 330 psi to zero & check floats. Pressure increased to 330 psi (floats not holding). Planned TOC in annulus at 30700'. Observed no lift pressure during cement displacement w/ 10% returns. Close lower annular & monitor backside pressure while WOC. Bled off remaining drill pipe pressure & check floats (floats holding). Drop 2-3/4" Versaflex hanger setting ball & allow to free fall to ball seat.","WAR_START_DT":"2016-11-27","WELL_NAME":"  004"},{"   ":111,"API12":608074032000,"TEXT_REMARK":"12/4/16 - Allow 2-3/4" Versaflex hanger setting ball to free fall onto ball seat while WOC. 12/5/16 - TIH w/ test plug assy f/ 5362' to 8625'. Land Dril-Quip test plug in wellhead w/ 110k down. Close annular & verify seat w/ 1000 psi. Bled pressure & open annular.
