12/6/16 - Cont'd testing BOPs & related equipment on 5" drill pipe w/ 15.9 ppg SBM. Tests performed f/ bridge panel on Blue POD SEM "B". Tested pipe rams to 250 / 11700 psi; annulars to 250 / 3500 psi & buffer manifold valves to 250 / 9000 psi for 5 min each. Function test BOPs on 5" drill pipe f/ bridge panel on Blue POD SEM "B" & driller's panel on Yellow POD SEM "B". Function diverter auto sequence f/ driller's STRB line. RD BOP test assy. TIH w/ 8-1/2" drilling assy f/ 8132' to 31618'. Flush C&K lines w/ 15.7 ppg SBM. Wash down w/ 8-1/2" drilling assy f/ 31618'. Tag TOC at 31841' & confirm w/ 15k down. Drill cement in shoe track f/ 31841' to 32110' w/ 15.7 ppg SBM. Wash down f/ 32110' to 32230'. Drill 10' of new formation f/ 32230' to 32240'. Pump back into the shoe at 32110'. Break circ down choke line & drill string. Close upper annular & verify space-out. Perform FIT w/ 15.7 ppg SBM at 31885' TVD shoe depth to 1490 psi (16.60 ppg EMW). Static PWD w/ probe depth at 31859' TVD was 16.85 ppg EMW.

12/7/16 - Pump up static PWD of 16.85 ppg EMW w/ MWD. Wash down f/ 32101' to 32240'. Troubleshoot MWD resistivity issues by logging back to shoe. Drill 8-1/2" hole f/ 32240' to 32274' w/ 15.7 ppg SBM. Experience erratic torque drilling on bottom. Pump back to 9-5/8" shoe to clear possible debris around BHA. Cont'd to troubleshoot MWD resistivity issues. Drill 8-1/2" hole f/ 32274' to 32317'. Unable to resolve MWD resistivity issues. Prepare to POOH & change 8-1/2" BHA. Circ w/ 15.7 ppg. Flow check well on trip tank; static. Main hydroracker stuck at well center; tail arm would not retract. Troubleshoot & repair tail arm on racker. RU OES flowback tool & bails. Pumped OOH f/ 32317' to 31486'. Troubleshoot OES flowback tool; tool would not retract off tool joint. RD OES flowback tool & bails. RU 1250T drilling bails & BX-5 elevators. Pump OOH using top drive f/ 31486' to 29509'.

12/8/16 - Cont'd to pump OOH using top drive f/ 29509' to 24716'. POOH w/ 4 stands wet f/ 24716' to 24188'; observed correct displacement. Pumped 115 bbls 17.8 ppg SBM slug. POOH f/ 24188' to 1063'.

12/9/16 - POOH f/ 1063' to surface. Troubleshoot main racker lower guide arm. Slip & cut 103' of drill line. Functioned UBSR; LBSR & CSR f/ bridge panel; Yellow Pod SEM B & driller's panel Blue Pod; SEM B. TIH w/ 8-1/2" BHA f/ surface to 1080'. Performed MWD shallow test; good test. TIH f/ 1080' to 30433'. 

12/10/16 - Cont'd TIH f/ 30433' to 32100'. Established circulation & logged down f/ 32100' to 32317'. Drill 8-1/2" directional hole f/ 32317' to 32954'. ","WAR_START_DT":"2016-12-04","WELL_NAME":"  004"},{"   ":112,"API12":608074032000,"TEXT_REMARK":"12/11/16 - Drill 8-1/2" directional hole f/ 32954' to 33668' w/ 15.7 ppg SBM.

12/15/16 - Cont'd TOOH f/ 10645' to 1206'. Performed BHA shallow test; good test. TOOH f/ 1206' to 155'. Performed MWD data download. Well static. TOOH to surface. MU new 8-1/2" bit. Well static. f/ 34213 to 34660'.

12/19/16 - Cont'd TOOH f/ 25542' to 21583'. RD OES tool & service loop. TOOH f/ 21583' to 6117'. MU BOP test assy & chicksan to workstring. Space out 5" drill pipe
across BOP stack. Tested BOP & related equipment on 5" drill pipe w/ 16.0 ppg SBM f/ driller's control panel; Yellow POD; SEM "A". Tested pipe rams to 250 / 11700 psi; annulars to 250 / 3500 psi & buffer manifold valves to 250 / 9000 psi for 5 min each.

28573'. Washed cement stringers & soft cement f/ 28573' to 32711'. Worked through cement stringers as required. Losses began to occur at 3.5 bpm. Boost riser at 455 gpm. POOH 1 stand & circ'd at 200 gpm / 1778 psi to circ cement cuttings up hole.

3/25/17 - Pumped OOH f/ 32673' to 32295' w/ 16.2 ppg SOBM. Circ'd w/ 16.2 ppg SOBM. Losses occured. Spotted 260 bbls of 12.3 ppg SOBM in riser w/ boost line to try to limit losses while circulating. 3/28/17 - Washed down w/ 11-7/8" FasDrill cement retainer f/ 31374' to 31545' w/ 16.2 ppg SOBM. FasDrill retainer set inadvertently at 31545' while washing in hole. Circ'd at 420 gpm / 3100 psi w/ 16.2 ppg SOBM to clean up mud. Stung into retainer & put 30k lbs down. Broke circ down choke line. Closed upper annular & put 1500 psi on backside. Pressure held & had no communication to drill string. Open upper annular. Recorded injection rates w/ rig pump using 16.2 ppg SOBM: 1 bpm / 945 psi; 2 bpm / 1170 psi; 3 bpm / 1400 psi; 4 bpm / 1630 psi; 5 bpm / 1860 psi. Unstung f/ FasDrill & pulled up to 31525'. Cement unit circ'd 10 bbls of 16.5 ppg tuned spacer. Tested lines to 7500 psi. Pumped 190 bbls of 16.5 ppg Tuned Spacer; 20 bbls Fresh Water; 25 bbls CaCl; 20 bbls Fresh Water; 25 bbls of FloCheck & 20 bbls Fresh Water. M&P 216 bbls / 1213 cuft / 911 sx of 17.0 ppg cement slurry followed by 20 bbls of 16.5 ppg Tuned Spacer & 20 bbls of 16.2 ppg SOBM. Displaced cement w/ rig pumps w/ 215 bbls of 16.2 ppg SOBM. Stopped pumps; stung into FasDrill retainer & closed upper annular. Applied 1000 psi on back side. Squeezed 500 bbls below retainer w/ 16.2 ppg SOBM at 7 bpm / 1800 psi. Slight squeeze pressure was seen at end of squeeze. Bled off backside pressure & opened annular. RD cement stand & cement line. Unstung f/ FasDrill & displaced 5 bbls of cement on top of FasDrill. Cement in place at 10:30 hrs. TOOH f/ 31545' to 29522'. CBU f/ 29522' w/ 16.2 ppg SOBM. Pumped 140 bbl of 18.1 ppg slug & POOH f/ 29522' to 20822'. 

3/29/17 - Function tested BOP f/ bridge panel; yellow pod & driller panel; blue pod on 6-5/8" DP. Function tested diverter f/ bridge panel starboard. Good test. Tested all BSR / CSR to 250 / 1200 psi for 5 min each w/ 16.2 ppg SOBM recorded on Greenlight & Halliburton chart. All good tests. TIH w/ hydraulic seal assy retrieval tool to 5965'. Set 50k lbs down & put 1 left hand turn into string w/ 5k ftlbs tq. Closed lower annular & pulled seal assy w/ 5k lbs overpull. Opened choke line to monitoring tank & monitored for gain/loss; well static. Opened lower annular & monitored on trip tank; well static. TOOH w/ hydraulic seal assy retrieval tool & recovered seal assy f/ 5965' to 1321'. Note: Only recovered the lockdown sleeve f/ the seal assy. Dril-Quip engineering confirmed that remainder of seal assy can be pulled together w/ liner hanger.

3/30/17 - POOH w/ seal assy retrieval tool to surface. MU Dril-Quip lead impression block & TIH to 5861'. Land impression block in wellhead w/ 50k down. Stage pumps to 2500 psi & hold for 15 min. POOH w/ lead impression tool f/ 5861' to 3957'. MU lockdown sleeve to tailpipe. TIH w/ wellhead lockdown sleeve f/ 3957' to 8596'. Fill drill string w/ 16.2 ppg SBM. Land lockdown sleeve in wellhead & confirm w/ 170k down. Stage pumps to 3500 psi & hold for 5 min. Bled off pressure. Repeat pressure cycle. Bled off pressure & confirm sleeve set w/ 50k overpull. Shear running tool f/ lockdown sleeve w/ 75k overpull. Pump 50 bbl slug of 18.2 ppg. POOH w/ Dril-Quip lockdown running tool f/ 8596' to 3957'. Pump 30 bbl slug of 18.2 ppg. POOH w/ 6-5/8" tailpipe f/ 3957' to surface. MU casing cutter assy & TIH f/ surface to 4690'. Encountered tight spot at 4690'. Work cutter assy f/ 4690' to 4732'.

3/31/17 - TIH w/ 14" casing cutter assy f/ 4732' to 6583'. Land swivel in wellhead & confirm w/ 15k down. Cut 14" casing at 6669'. POOH w/ 14" cutter assy f/ 6669' to surface. MU Dril-Quip bull nose jet sub & lockdown retrieval tool. TIH on 6-5/8" drill pipe f/ surface to 5971'. Land lockdown retrieval tool in wellhead w/ 50k down. Take 20k overpull & confirm retrieval tool locked in position. Pressure up to 2500 psi & hold for 5 min. Bled off & repeat pressure cycle. Pull lockdown sleeve w/ 62k overpull. Pump 50 bbl slug of 18.2 ppg. POOH w/ lockdown retrieval assy to surface. MU Dril-Quip hanger seal retrieval tool (HSRT) & TIH f/ 1321' to 5959'. Land HSRT in wellhead w/ 20k down. Take 20k overpull & confirm latch into seal assy. Slack off 50k & put 1/2 left-hand turn in string w/ 3k torque. Close lower annular & pull seal assy w/ 35k overpull. Open lower annular & monitor well on trip tank. Close lower annular & adjust riser cap down choke liner w/ 16.2 ppg.

4/1/17 - Close lower annular & adjust riser cap w/ 320 bbls of 16.2 ppg. POOH w/ HSRT f/ 5959' to surface. MU 14" casing spear & TIH on 6-5/8" drill pipe to 4635'. Position spear at 4715'. Engage 14" casing. Pull to 580k (195k over drill string weight) & observe free movement w/ 14" casing. POOH w/ 14" casing spear f/ 4715' to surface. Pull 14" casing hanger above rotary. RD BX-5 elevators & install casing elevators. POOH w/ 14" casing. RD casing handling equipment. MU polish mill assy & TIH to 6573'. Wash down f/ 6573'. Tag top of 14" casing at 6689' & confirm w/ 10k down. Begin polishing top of 14" casing. 4/4/17 - POOH w/ wear sleeve adapter f/ 5359' to surface. Test upper BSR & casing w/ 16.2 ppg SBM f/ bridge panel on Blue POD SEM "A" to 250 psi for 5 min then 1405 psi for 30 min. 6/13/17 - POOH f/ 4029' to surface. Blackhawk disconnect tool upper section recovered as expected; no issues w/ tool. Tested choke line f/ Halliburton unit to 3000 psi. Closed BSR & tested cement plug w/ Halliburton unit to 1500 psi w/ 16.1 ppg SOBM. Good
test. Opened BSR. MU 14" Blackhawk CIBP. RIH w/ CIBP f/ surface to 21700' & tagged TOL w/ 3k lbs. Washed CIBP setting area. Set CIBP at 21700'. Pull tested to 50k lbs & weight tested to 30k lbs. 6/15/17 - TOOH f/ 5174' to surface. Tested cement plug against UBSR w/ Halliburton cement unit to 1500 psi for 15 min on chart w/ 16.1 ppg SOBM. Good test. TIH w/ RTTS packer f/ surface to 5290'. Washed setting area. Set RTTS packer at 5290'. Tested  inner ball valve to 1000 psi. Released f/ RTTS. Closed upper annular & tested RTTS f/ above to 1000 psi. Good tests. Performed negative test to 8.6 ppg EMW at mud line w/ 92 bbls of 6.6 ppg base oil (1823 psi differential pressure) down drill string. Closed MPR & bled off pressure to 0 psi & monitored on stripper tank for 30 min. Good
test. Pressured back up to 1825 psi & opened MPR. Displaced well f/ 16.1 ppg SOBM to 8.6 ppg SW. Performed flowcheck once well all SW; static. Flushed Mil Clean soap pill through C&K manifold; mud gas seperator; cement test line; trip tanks & all other surface lines. MU cement line. Pumped 10 bbl FW & tested lines to 3000 psi for 5 min. Good Test. Pumped 10 bbl FW ahead. M&P 75 bbl / 415 cuft / 285 sx of 16.4 ppg Class H silica slurry; yield: 1.462 cuft/sx. Displaced cement w/ 10 bbls of FW & 75 bbls of SW. Cement in place at 1830 hrs. Calculated TOC at 4790'. RD cement line & cement stand. Pull out of cement plug f/ 5290' to 4700'. CBU w/ wiper ball using 8.6 ppg SW. POOH f/ 4700' to surface. 

6/16/17 - Slipped & cut 136' of drill line. TIH w/ jet sub & riser brushes f/ surface to 4695. Jet BOP w/ 8.6 ppg SW f/ 4577' to 4695'. Flushed surface equipment w/ drill water. & LD diverter. RD BX-7 elevators & RU manual riser running tool. Performed BOP pre-retrieval checklist. PU landing joint & MU to slip jt inner barrel. Connected telescopic joint control lines.

6/17/17 - Hooked up hoses / control lines to slip joint. Locked slip joint. Took 50k lb overpull of inner barrel / locks. Unlatched BOP & lifted off WH. Primary & secondary unlatch used. ROV on bottom to monitor unlatch. Rig heading at unlatch = 325°. Moved rig 50' off location at 235°. Stowed tensioner ring. RD storm loops & drape hoses. LD riser landing jt. Landed out slip jt in spider. Unlocked slip joint; cleaned & serviced inner barrel. Cleaned slip jt & LD. RD manual riser RT & RU hydraulic riser RT. Pulled riser.
